window.SEARCH_INDEX = [{"kind":"notes","page":1,"title":"Notes page 1","text":"Book Of Revelation 1 •ORDER OF HOW REVELATION IS DELIVERED AND THE SUMMARIZED CONCLUSION OF REVELATION •THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION AND THE MYSTERY OF THE 7 STARS & 7 GOLDEN LAMPSTANDS 2 •THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT 3 •THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT 4 •THE THRONE OF HEAVEN IN THE SPIRITUAL REALM AND ITS ORGANIZATION 5 •THE BOOK SEALED WITH 7 SEALS 6 •THE END OF SUN, MOON, STARS 7 •THE CREATION OF THE SEALED 12 TRIBES AND THE GREAT MULTITUDE IN WHITE 8 •THE SOUND OF 7 TRUMPETS AND EVENTS WHICH THEY PROCLAIM 9 •THE MESSENGERS FROM THE ABYSS, AND DEATH 10 •THE OPEN WORD FROM HEAVEN AND THE MYSTERY OF THE 7th TRUMPET 11 •TWO WITNESSES AND THE 7th TRUMPET 12 •THE VICTORY OF THE CHILD WHO WILL RULE OVER THE NATIONS 13 •THE CHOSEN PEOPLE WHO BETRAYED AND RECEIVED THE MARK OF THE BEAST 14 •THE HARVESTED AND SEALED 144.000 OF THE 12 TRIBES OF MT.ZION 15 •THE TEMPLE OF THE TABERNACLE OF THE TESTIMONY WHERE ALL NATIONS WILL WORSHIP 16 •7 BOWLS OF WRATH 17 •WINE OF ADULTERIES, AND THE MYSTERY OF THE PROSTITUTE AND THE BEAST 18 •BABYLON, HOME OF DEMONS AND ALL FALLEN NATIONS 19 •THE WEDDING BANQUET OF THE LAMB 20 •THE MILLENNIAL CITY, THE FIRST RESURRECTION 21 •THE NEW HEAVEN AND NEW EARTH, AND THE HOLY CITY 22 •THE TREE OF LIFE AND THE LORD'S MESSENGER"},{"kind":"notes","page":2,"title":"Notes page 2","text":"Physical Fulfillment Figures Kim Jong-kyu 김종규 Head of Hosaeng Prayer House Yu In-su 유인수 Doctor & Yu In-gu's brother Hong Jong-hyo 홍종효 Reed (Rv11) Lee Hui-chun 이희춘 Choi Byeong-jun 최병준 2Horns (Rv13:11) Diverse"},{"kind":"notes","page":3,"title":"Notes page 3","text":"REVELATION 1: THE ORDER OF HOW REVELATION IS DELIVERED AND THE SUMMARIZED CONCLUSION OF REVELATION Rev 1:1-8 1 The revelation of Jesus Christ, which God gave him to show his servants what must soon take place. He made it known by sending his angel to his servant John, 2 who testifies to everything he saw--that is, the word of God and the testimony of Jesus Christ. 3 Blessed is the one who reads the words of this prophecy, and blessed are those who hear it and take to heart what is written in it, because the time is near. 4 John, To the seven churches in the province of Asia: Grace and peace to you from him who is, and who was, and who is to come, and from the seven spirits before his throne, 5 and from Jesus Christ, who is the faithful witness, the firstborn from the dead, and the ruler of the kings of the earth. To him who loves us and has freed us from our sins by his blood, 6 and has made us to be a kingdom and priests to serve his God and Father--to him be glory and power for ever and ever! Amen. 7 Look, he is coming with the clouds, and every eye will see him, even those who pierced him; and all the peoples of the earth will mourn because of him. So shall it be! Amen. 8 \"I am the Alpha and the Omega,\" says the Lord God, \"who is, and who was, and who is to come, the Almighty.\" Definition of Revelation: To open & show Types of Revelation: By content: Vision (prophecy) & Physical (fulfillment). By era: O.T & N.T. [⋆False Revelation] O.T. Revelation Delivery Order Isa29:9-13 (Sealed book: parable- deep sleep) Hab2:2-3 (Appointed time: prophecies will be fulfilled) Ez1-3 (Chosen people exiled by gentile → Son of Man eat scroll → rebellious Israelites) Mt15:24 (Jesus sent to lost sheep of Israel → prophecy fulfilled) N.T. Revelation Delivery Order Rv5:1 (God's right hand: sealed book) Rv5:7 (Jesus takes the scroll) Rv6+8 (Begin breaking the seals) Rv10:1-2 (Angel) Rv10:8-10 (John) Rv10:11 (Servants) Importance of Revelation Jn17:3 (Eternal life by knowing true God and the sent) Mt11:27 (No one knows Father except Son & those to whom the Son chooses to reveal him) Gal3: 23-29 (Those who believe → Heirs of God) \"What must soon take place\" All events of revelation (Rv1-22) \"Servants\" receiving revelation 144.000 & Great Multitude in White (Those who hear & take it to heart) \"Word of God\" ○1 Moses time: Moses law ○2 F.C.: Open scroll: Lamentations, mourning, woes (Ez2-3) → Dry bones: Jerusalem (Ez37) ○3 S.C.: Open scroll (revealed word) John received (Rv10) \"Testimony of Jesus Christ\" Word that fulfilled the prophecy → What John has seen → Word of physical fulfillment \"Everything John saw\" Revelation 1-22 (Rv22:8) 1 The revelation of Jesus Christ, which God gave him to show his servants what must soon take place. He made it known by sending his angel to his servant John, 2 who testifies to everything he saw--that is, the word of God and the testimony of Jesus Christ. 3 Blessed is the one who reads the words of this prophecy, and blessed are those who hear it and take to heart what is written in it, because the time is near. 4 John, To the seven churches in the province of Asia: Grace and peace to you from him who is, and who was, and who is to come, and from the seven spirits before his throne, 5 and from Jesus Christ, who is the faithful witness, the firstborn from the dead, and the ruler of the kings of the earth. To him who loves us and has freed us from our sins by his blood, 6 and has made us to be a kingdom and priests to serve his God and Father--to him be glory and power for ever and ever! Amen. 7 Look, he is coming with the clouds, and every eye will see him, even those who pierced him; and all the peoples of the earth will mourn because of him. So shall it be! Amen. 8 \"I am the Alpha and the Omega,\" says the Lord God, \"who is, and who was, and who is to come, the Almighty.\""},{"kind":"notes","page":4,"title":"Notes page 4","text":"\"One who reads\" One who can explain plainly → One who received the word in Rv10 = OWO He can testify what he has seen & heard because he was at the place of event! (cf. Mt24:15) \"One who hear\" Peoples, nations, languages, kings (Congregations, churches, doctrines, pastors) (Rv10:11) \"One who take it to heart\" Servants: 144.000 + GMW (Those who keep it) \"Things written in it\" The words of promise (\"it\" = Book of Revelation) Blessings for those who keep it Eternal life \"Seven churches\" 7 golden lampstands (7 messengers) \"Province of Asia\" Parable for Gwacheon, since 7 churches are there! (\"Minor Asia\": Greece, Turkey) Letters sent in whose name ○1 God (Rv4:8) ○2 Seven spirits before Gods throne (Rv3:1) ○3 Jesus (Rv2:1) Effect of the blood of Jesus (1) Rv1:5-6: Free us from our sins & make us to be a kingdom and priests (2) Rv5:9-10: Make us to be a kingdom and priests [purchased from every tribe, language, people, nation= sea (Rv17:5)] (3) Rv7:14: Great multitude in white (who washed their robes and made them white) (4) Rv12:11: Weapon (overcame dragon by the blood of the lamb and the word of testimony) (5) Rv19:13: Weapon to fight and overcome (dressed with robe dipped in blood) \"Coming with the clouds\"Jesus coming as spirit (Act1:9-11) and with spirits (4 living creatures: role to judge in Rv6) \"Every eye will see him\" People in tabernacle temple will see Jesus: Seeing OWO is seeing Jesus (Jn14:9-10) \"Mourn because of Jesus\" ○1 First tabernacle who betrayed ○2 Who don't believe revelation (since about to be judged) [Content of Rv1:7 connected to Rv11:12] \"Alpha & Omega\" Work of restoration which began after Adam's fall will be full completed as revelation is fulfilled: Every prophecy from Genesis to Revelation will be fulfilled! (Rv1:8,Rv21:6,Rv22:13) Prophecy Fulfillment Who Apostle John New John (OWO) When 2000 years ago Time of Revelation Where Island Patmos 경기도 시흥군 과천면 막계리 What Vision (what must soon take place) B-D-S (physical events) Why To believe when it happens (Jn14:29) Believe→ Eternal Life & Salvation How Vision Physical Fulfillment (plainly) Promised pastor: Lee Man-hee (이만희) Verse New John Rv1:2 One who reads Rv1:3 Brother Rv1:9 One on whom Jesus placed his right hand Rv1:17 One who overcomes & One who sends letters Rv2-3 One who receives open scroll from angel Rv10:8-10 7th Trumpet Rv11:15 Male child Rv12:5 One who overcome by blood of Lamb & word of testimony Rv12:7-11 Bride Rv19:7 White horse Rv19:11 He who overcomes: Son Rv21:7 One who heard and saw Rv22:8 Angel (messenger) sent to churches Rv22:16 Faithful & wise servant Mt24:45-47 Counselor (advocate) Jn14-16"},{"kind":"notes","page":5,"title":"Notes page 5","text":"REVELATION 1: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION AND THE MYSTERY OF THE 7 STARS & 7 GOLDEN LAMPSTANDS Rev1:9-20 \"Island Patmos\" Tabernacle Temple which didn't belong to any denomination of the world (sea) \"Brother\" New John was trained & brought up by same word as 7 messengers received from Jesus \"Lord's Day\" Day when Jesus appeared to John (1977) \"Seven golden lampstands\" Tabernacle temple Jesus shows John his image To let 7 messengers (who saw it during their training) know that letters are sent from Jesus \"Someone like a son of man\" Jesus' transfigured image (spiritual image) \"Double-edged sword\" Word (power to judge betrayer & destroyer) \"Fell at his feet \" He was scared of dreadful appearance of transfigured Jesus \"Placed his right hand on John\" Jesus anointed John as new pastor instead of 7 messengers \"Keys of death and Hades\" Key (wisdom/authority), death (Authority/power of Satan), Hades (Satan's dwelling place) ○1 Jesus: Salvation (Rv1:18) ○2 Wormwood: Judge betrayers (Rv9:1-3) ○3 Angel: Seize & lock up the dragon into the Abyss (Rv20:1-3) \"What you have seen\" Appearance of Jesus, 7 stars, 7 golden lampstands \"What is now\" Satan's deception \"What will take place later\" Conditional promise (if you overcome you will receive 12 blessings) \"Mystery of 7 stars & 7 g. l.\" 7 messengers didn't know that they are betrayer and even called themselves the 7 stars 9 I, John, your brother and companion in the suffering and kingdom and patient endurance that are ours in Jesus, was on the island of Patmos because of the word of God and the testimony of Jesus. 10 On the Lord's Day I was in the Spirit, and I heard behind me a loud voice like a trumpet, 11 which said: \"Write on a scroll what you see and send it to the seven churches: to Ephesus, Smyrna, Pergamum, Thyatira, Sardis, Philadelphia and Laodicea.\" 12 I turned around to see the voice that was speaking to me. And when I turned I saw seven golden lampstands, 13 and among the lampstands was someone \"like a son of man,\" dressed in a robe reaching down to his feet and with a golden sash around his chest. 14 His head and hair were white like wool, as white as snow, and his eyes were like blazing fire. 15 His feet were like bronze glowing in a furnace, and his voice was like the sound of rushing waters. 16 In his right hand he held seven stars, and out of his mouth came a sharp double-edged sword. His face was like the sun shining in all its brilliance. 17 When I saw him, I fell at his feet as though dead. Then he placed his right hand on me and said: \"Do not be afraid. I am the First and the Last. 18 I am the Living One; I was dead, and behold I am alive for ever and ever! And I hold the keys of death and Hades. 19 \"Write, therefore, what you have seen, what is now and what will take place later. 20 The mystery of the seven stars that you saw in my right hand and of the seven golden lampstands is this: The seven stars are the angels of the seven churches, and the seven lampstands are the seven churches."},{"kind":"notes","page":6,"title":"Notes page 6","text":"Korean Name English Name Spiritual Name Characteristics 유인구 Ryu In Gu Immanuel \"Greater light\" (Sun); Head of 7 stars; Father of Samson; Running hospital without license; Husband of Moses' sister; Studied music in China & worked in circus for Moses; Died 1984; cf.Saul:1st king 유재열 Ryu Jae Yeol Samson \"Lesser light\" (Moon); Son of Immanuel; Gymnastic; 18 years old; Woman dressed in sun moon stars (Rv12:1); cf. David:2nd king 김창도 Kim Chang Do Michael Gangster in노량진; Samson's bodyguard; left 1980 Sep. 정창래 Jung Chang Rye Samuel Good at praying; Polio; left 1980 Sep. 김영애 Kim Young Ae Debora Only woman; Bachelorette; Could not bear children; Adopted son Nam Kwang Hyun (Nehemiah) tried to stab SSN; left 1980 Sep. 백만봉 Paik Man bong Solomon Shoe-shiner; left 1969 Nov. cf. Church of Sardis (Rv3:1-6): New Tabernacle Church 신광일 Shin Gwang Il Joshua Moses' son; Came to SCJ; Country boy; 18 years old; left 1969 Nov. cf. Church of Philadelphia (Rv3:7-13, Zech3) 신종환 Shin Jong Hwan Moses Elder; 1985 declared that Shin Gwang Il is 2nd Jesus & left tabern."},{"kind":"notes","page":7,"title":"Notes page 7","text":"REVELATION 2: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rev 2:1-7 (Church in Ephesus) Appearance of Jesus ○1 Holding 7 stars in his right hand (Rv1:16) ○2 Walking among 7 golden lampstands (Rv1:13) \"Forsaken first love\" Jesus who appointed them as his pastors and brought them up → 2 sins (Jer2:13,Ho10:10) ○1 Abandoning God's word = Betraying pastor who was appointed by God ○2Broken cistern = bottomless pit = Abyss = dungeon = hell → Organization of Satan →7 messengers broke the covenant with Jesus & became one with Nicolaitans (destroyer) \"Height from which fallen\" ○1 Fallen from Jesus right hand ○2 Their affiliation changed from God's to Satan's side \"Remove lampstand from place\" ○1 Lampstand: 7 spirits before God's throne (Rv4:5) [7eyes:role as inspectors (Rv5:6)] ○2 Removing lampstand: Take away 7 spirits which came upon 7 messengers → 7 spirits moved to 7 horns (7 workers newly appointed by Jesus) [cf.Zech4] \"Nicolaitans\" Group of Satan = 7+10 beast (Rv13) = Babylon → Stewardship Education Center [cf.Gal4:1-2] ○1 Nicolas (Acts6:5): One of 7 deacons; Gentile converted to Judaism [cf.Mt24:15-16] ○2 Pastor Oh: Catholic pastor → Presbyterian Church → Tabernacle Temple → They could not banish the Nicolaitans from tabernacle even though they hate them since 7 messengers became mute dogs- couldn't bark as they took bribes from them (Isa56:9-12) Blessings for OWO \"Fruit of tree of life in paradise\" Fruit of tree of life in kingdom of God : Revealed word (Rv1:1, Rv10:1-2 & 8-10) ○1 Paradise: Spiritual realm where God dwells (Rv4) = Third Heaven (2Cor12:1-4) First Heaven: First Tabernacle (Rv21:1) Second Heaven: New Heaven = Mt. Zion (Rv21:1) ○2 Tree of life: Jesus (Jn14:6, Jn15:1) ○3 Fruit of tree of life: Word of life given by Jesus (Pv18:20-21) 1 \"To the angel of the church in Ephesus write: These are the words of him who holds the seven stars in his right hand and walks among the seven golden lampstands: 2 I know your deeds, your hard work and your perseverance. I know that you cannot tolerate wicked men, that you have tested those who claim to be apostles but are not, and have found them false. 3 You have persevered and have endured hardships for my name, and have not grown weary. 4 Yet I hold this against you: You have forsaken your first love. 5 Remember the height from which you have fallen! Repent and do the things you did at first. If you do not repent, I will come to you and remove your lampstand from its place. 6 But you have this in your favor: You hate the practices of the Nicolaitans, which I also hate. 7 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. To him who overcomes, I will give the right to eat from the tree of life, which is in the paradise of God."},{"kind":"notes","page":8,"title":"Notes page 8","text":"REVELATION 2: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rv2:8-11 (Church in Smyrna) Appearance of Jesus ○1 The First and the Last (Rv1:17) ○2 The one who died and came to life again (Rv1:18) \"Afflictions & poverty\" They do not have any worldly pastor certificates (2Cor6:10) \"Rich\" Received the words and positions from Jesus which anyone else in world cannot possess \"Synagogue of Satan\" Satan's organization = 7heads+10horns = Nicolaitans ○1 Those who pretend to be righteous workers (2Cor11:13-15) ○2 The wolves masquerading as sheep (Mt7:15) ○3 False Christs and prophets (Mt24:24-25) \"Put some of you in prison\" ○1 Devil: Satan's pastor (Pastor Oh) \"Persecution for 10 days\" ○2 Some of you: Some evangelists of tabernacle temple ○3 Prison: Abyss (hell) ○4 Being put in prison: Preventing someone from attending a church by gentile laws ○5 Put in prison because they opposed pastor Oh to rule the tabernacle in place of Mr Ryu → Some evangelists could not attend tabernacle temple because they were sentenced to probation for 10 days by Presbyterian laws (around September 1981) [Event related to event of 5th trumpet in Rv9] Cf. Daniel & 3 friends (Dn1):  Royal family & nobles (evangelists & elders)  Exiled into Babylon & tested for 10 days  Only eat vegetables instead of Babylonian food Blessings for OWO \"Crown of life\" Eternal life (crown: glory/honor/position) \"Not hurt by second death\" ○1 Second death (Rv20:15, Rv21:8) Fiery lake of burning sulfur & place where our spirits will be tormented for ever and ever ○2 Those not hurt by second death: Who take part in first resurrection (Rv20:4-6) ○3 Those hurt by second death:  Those whose names not written in book of life  Cowardly, murderers, sexually immoral, idolaters, liars (Rv21:8, Rv22:15) 8 \"To the angel of the church in Smyrna write: These are the words of him who is the First and the Last, who died and came to life again. 9 I know your afflictions and your poverty--yet you are rich! I know the slander of those who say they are Jews and are not, but are a synagogue of Satan. 10 Do not be afraid of what you are about to suffer. I tell you, the devil will put some of you in prison to test you, and you will suffer persecution for ten days. Be faithful, even to the point of death, and I will give you the crown of life. 11 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. He who overcomes will not be hurt at all by the second death."},{"kind":"notes","page":9,"title":"Notes page 9","text":"REVELATION 2: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rv2:12-17 (Church in Pergamum) Appearance of Jesus One who has the sharp, double-edged sword (Rv1:16): Word of judgment (Eph6:12-17) \"Where you live Satan has throne\" Tabernacle temple has been changed into throne of Satan because he overtook tabernacle ○1 F.C.: Teacher of law+ Pharisees on Moses seat (Mt23:2). Tabern.: Gods temple (Jerusalem) ○2 S.C.: 7+10 beast invade & overtake tabernacle (Rv13). Tabern: Gods temple (7g.l. tabern.) \"Antipas\" Figure (2000y ago) who kept faith to the end even though he was in Satan's dwelling place →Like him, Jesus would require 7 messengers to keep their faith to the end no matter what \"Balaam\" ○1 Gentile man who worked as a prophet of God = the one like Nicolas (Acts6:5) ○2 Loved the wages of wickedness & left the straight way→rebuked by a donkey (2Pt2:15-16) ○3 Mr Oh: Worked as pastor on God's side & later became one with Satan to destroy tabern. \"Balak\" ○1 King of Moab [King: pastor (1Pt2:9)/ Moab: gentile nation= gentile church] ○2 Head/representative pastor of group of Satan (Nicolaitan): Mr Tak-Great Prostitute (Rv17) \"Balam & Balak\" Balak called Balaam to curse the Israelites because he was afraid they might destroy his land. He didn't allow them to pass through land of Moab & tried to destroy them by making plots through Balaam who became blind to money & became one with Balak & taught him the way to defeat them (Nu22-25). Israelites committed adulteries with Moab women→ God's plagues→24000 died (Nu25, Nu31:16, Jo24:9) Balaam was killed by Moses' sword (Nu31:8) \"Food sacrificed to idols\" Satan's doctrines made by men's thoughts \"Sexual immorality\" Receiving seed (word) of Satan & following the teachings of Satan's pastor \"Teaching of Nicolaitans\" Commentaries made by Babylon (=maddening wine of adulteries) Blessings for OWO \"Hidden manna\" Words of the secret of kingdom of God which have been hidden in parables (Mt13:34-35) ○1 Physical Israel: Physical manna coming from heaven where God dwells-die (Ex16, Nu11) ○2 Spiritual Israel: Flesh& blood of Jesus (living bread)-die→ live again at last day (Jn6:53-57) ○3 New spiritual Israel: Revealed word (Rv10)-obtain eternal life & live for ever and ever \"White stone\" Word of judgment [cf. O.T.: Stone tablets. F.C.: Living stone-Jesus (Mt21:42-44)] ○1 God's judgment to let people cleanse themselves from sins: Judgment for revival ○2 God's judgment is true & just (righteous): Acc. to Bible & what they have done (Rv20:12) \"New name written on it\" Jesus' new name (Rv3:12) [○1Word (Jn1:1,1Jn1:1) ○2Title/Position (Lk1:17/Jn5:43/Jn14:26)] →○1 New word revealed in Rv10 ○2 OWO would give judgment to people instead of Jesus 12 \"To the angel of the church in Pergamum write: These are the words of him who has the sharp, double-edged sword. 13 I know where you live--where Satan has his throne. Yet you remain true to my name. You did not renounce your faith in me, even in the days of Antipas, my faithful witness, who was put to death in your city--where Satan lives. 14 Nevertheless, I have a few things against you: You have people there who hold to the teaching of Balaam, who taught Balak to entice the Israelites to sin by eating food sacrificed to idols and by committing sexual immorality. 15 Likewise you also have those who hold to the teaching of the Nicolaitans. 16 Repent therefore! Otherwise, I will soon come to you and will fight against them with the sword of my mouth. 17 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. To him who overcomes, I will give some of the hidden manna. I will also give him a white stone with a new name written on it, known only to him who receives it."},{"kind":"notes","page":10,"title":"Notes page 10","text":"REVELATION 2: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rv2:18-29 (Church in Thyatira) Appearance of Jesus Eyes like blazing fire & feet like burnished bronze (Rv1:15) \"Now doing more than at first\" They began God's work just in one church, but then they had around 80 branch churches \"Woman Jezebel\" Figure at time of Elijah who called herself prophetess (1Ki16:31-33) ○1 Daughter of king Ethbaal. Incited husband Ahab to worship Baal & killed many prophets ○2 Great Prostitute (Rv17)= Head pastor of Nicolaitans who ruled over all nations: Mr Tak ○3 Mislead God's servants (here: pastors & congregation members of tabernacle temple) \"Given her time to repent\" She was greatly shaken after hearing word of testimony, but didn't repent (Rv17:6) \"Bed of suffering\" 2nd death=fiery lake of burning sulfur (Rv21:8, Rv20:12) Judgm. decided while alive (Rv19:20) \"Suffer intensely\" 3 Plagues to those who commit adultery with her [Seal (Rv6), trumpet (Rv8,9), bowl (Rv16)] \"Strike her children dead\" Congregation of tabernacle judged with word of judgment & their spirits (words) die (Rv18:8) Contrast Rv6:8: Chosen ppl killed by destroyers while fall of Babylon by God's plagues (Rv16) \"Rest of you in Thyatira\" Those who did not become one with Nicolaitans (group of Satan) \"A few people in white clothes\" (Rv3:4) \"A quart of wheat & three quarts of barley\" (Rv6:6) \"Satan's deep secrets\" Secretive plots to destroy & devour the tabernacle temple →Mr Oh came to tabernacle with plan to devour it & make it to be his own possession \"What you have\" Word & position of authority Blessings for OWO \"Iron scepter\" Authority to rule ○1 Prophecy: God will give iron scepter to his son (Ps2:6-9) ○2 Jesus was given iron scepter to rule over all nations from God (Jn17:2) ○3 Jesus gave iron scepter to OWO (Rv2:26-27) →Condition: Fight & overcome dragon (Rv12:7-9) \"Morning star\" Jesus (Rv22:16) → Jesus will get married to OWO & live together with him forever (Rv19: Bride of the Lamb) 18 \"To the angel of the church in Thyatira write: These are the words of the Son of God, whose eyes are like blazing fire and whose feet are like burnished bronze. 19 I know your deeds, your love and faith, your service and perseverance, and that you are now doing more than you did at first. 20 Nevertheless, I have this against you: You tolerate that woman Jezebel, who calls herself a prophetess. By her teaching she misleads my servants into sexual immorality and the eating of food sacrificed to idols. 21 I have given her time to repent of her immorality, but she is unwilling. 22 So I will cast her on a bed of suffering, and I will make those who commit adultery with her suffer intensely, unless they repent of her ways. 23 I will strike her children dead. Then all the churches will know that I am he who searches hearts and minds, and I will repay each of you according to your deeds. 24 Now I say to the rest of you in Thyatira, to you who do not hold to her teaching and have not learned Satan's so-called deep secrets (I will not impose any other burden on you): 25 Only hold on to what you have until I come. 26 To him who overcomes and does my will to the end, I will give authority over the nations-- 27 'He will rule them with an iron scepter; he will dash them to pieces like pottery'-just as I have received authority from my Father. 28 I will also give him the morning star. 29 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches."},{"kind":"notes","page":11,"title":"Notes page 11","text":"REVELATION 3: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rv3:1-6 (Church in Sardis) Appearance of Jesus Holds the 7 spirits of God and the 7 stars (Rv1:16) \"Reputation being alive but dead\" Being unable to testify Gods word, though they have it because gentile overtook them (Rv13) ○1 Reputation: Title/position of authority ○2 Being alive: Having Gods word = life (Jn1:1-4) → Death of their spirit & task \"What remains about to die\" Their faith is likely to disappear if they don't keep it firmly \"What you received & heard\" Word of God given from the Holy Spirit Trained & educated by Holy Spirit, not by the world, and chosen & appointed as God's pastors \"Coming like a thief\" When? After sun, moon, stars fall & darken (Mt24:29-31) To whom like a thief? Sons of darkness (1Thes5:1-6) [Appears 6 times in N.T: Mt24:43, Lk12:39, 1Thes5:2, 1Thes5:4, Rv3:3, Rv16:15] \"A few people in Sardis\" Remnant seed (Is1:9)= 1 quart of wheat & 3 quarts of barley (Rv6:6) → cf. Solomon left tabernacle & established his own church (Recreation Church). Some ppl from tabernacle, who were fellow workers of promised pastor, joined Solomon. After promised pastor received word from Jesus he went there & delivered the word to his former colleagues→ A few listened & accompanied him \"Not soiled their clothes\" Not committed adultery with women (false pastors) nor accepted gentile doctrines (Rv14:4) [Clothes: Words/Deeds (Rv19:13, Rv19:8)] \"They will walk with Jesus\" Accompany with the one who was chosen & anointed as God's pastor by Jesus Blessings for OWO \"White clothes\" Word of truth & righteous acts (Rv19:8, Rv19:13) [→to be acknowledged by God/Jesus] \"Name in book of life\" Book of Life: Registration book of the church that would be led by OWO (NHNE) [Appears 6 times in N.T: Rv3:5, Rv13:8, Rv17:8, Rv20:12, Rv20:15, Rv21:27] Place where book of life is: ○1 Before God's throne (Rv20:12) ○2 God, Jesus, kingdom of heaven (God's throne) → OWO (Rv3:12) ○3 Sing new song before the throne: Mt Zion where throne of God is (Rv14:3) 3 kinds of people: ○1 Being recorded firmly & completely in the book of life ○2 Not being recorded in the book of life [Written in dust=world=Babylon (Jer17:13)] [cf. Adam chosen from dust → return to dust (Gn3:19)] ○3 Being recorded at first but finally being blotted out from it (Ps69:28) 1 \"To the angel of the church in Sardis write: These are the words of him who holds the seven spirits of God and the seven stars. I know your deeds; you have a reputation of being alive, but you are dead. 2 Wake up! Strengthen what remains and is about to die, for I have not found your deeds complete in the sight of my God. 3 Remember, therefore, what you have received and heard; obey it, and repent. But if you do not wake up, I will come like a thief, and you will not know at what time I will come to you. 4 Yet you have a few people in Sardis who have not soiled their clothes. They will walk with me, dressed in white, for they are worthy. 5 He who overcomes will, like them, be dressed in white. I will never blot out his name from the book of life, but will acknowledge his name before my Father and his angels. 6 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches."},{"kind":"notes","page":12,"title":"Notes page 12","text":"REVELATION 3: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rv3:7-13 (Church in Philadelphia) Appearance of Jesus Holy and true, who holds the key of David (Is22:22) \"Key of David\" Wisdom that can open & shut the secret of the kingdom of heaven ○1 House of David: City of Zion = Jerusalem (physically) = Tabernacle (spiritually) (Is33:20) → Jerusalem or tabernacle represents kingdom of heaven spiritually! ○2 Key: Wisdom & authority to do something (Mt16:19, Mt18:18) ○3 Open: Explain something plainly/ Shut: Not interpreting → to hide something (in parables) \"Place open door before you\" They had forsaken God, still Jesus would like to open mindedly reason together (Is1:18) Door: Heart of man; here: Heart of Jesus (Jn10:7) [Rv3:9 related to Rv11:13] \"Hour of trial upon whole world\" Those who live on earth: Congregation members of tabernacle temple (Rv13:6) Whole world: Tabernacle temple including 80 branch churches [cf. \"astonished\" (Rv13:3)] Hour of trial: Prophesied time of betrayal & destruction Entity who tests: Nicolaitans = 7+10 = Group of Satan Tested: Being deceived/tempted [F.C.: Jesus was tested by Satan in a desert (Mt4)] \"Hold on what you have\" Word & title (position) \"So no one takes your crown\" Crown: Glory or honor or position → cf. high priest Joshua (Zech3): After Joshua (one of the 7 messengers) left the tabernacle, he would enter SCJ after long persuasion of promised pastor to make him return to God → he would receive new title & position in SCJ, but left SCJ soon after. Blessings for OWO \"Pillar in temple of God\" Entrusting important task (duty) to OWO [Duty to complete kingdom of heaven (Jn14:12)] Cf. Prophet Jeremiah: Fortified city, iron pillar, bronze wall (Jer1:17) \"Name of God, name of Holy city, New Jerusalem & Jesus' new name written on him\" ○1 God, Jesus and heaven will descend upon OWO (Mt13:31-32) ○2 OWO would become a house of God (heaven) in the physical world Cf. Great Prostitute: A home of demon (hell), a haunt for many dirty spirits (Rv17:5, Rv18:2-3) [Jesus' new name: New word & name of OWO (cf. Church in Pergamum)] 7 \"To the angel of the church in Philadelphia write: These are the words of him who is holy and true, who holds the key of David. What he opens no one can shut, and what he shuts no one can open. 8 I know your deeds. See, I have placed before you an open door that no one can shut. I know that you have little strength, yet you have kept my word and have not denied my name. 9 I will make those who are of the synagogue of Satan, who claim to be Jews though they are not, but are liars--I will make them come and fall down at your feet and acknowledge that I have loved you. 10 Since you have kept my command to endure patiently, I will also keep you from the hour of trial that is going to come upon the whole world to test those who live on the earth. 11 I am coming soon. Hold on to what you have, so that no one will take your crown. 12 Him who overcomes I will make a pillar in the temple of my God. Never again will he leave it. I will write on him the name of my God and the name of the city of my God, the new Jerusalem, which is coming down out of heaven from my God; and I will also write on him my new name. 13 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches."},{"kind":"notes","page":13,"title":"Notes page 13","text":"REVELATION 3: THE BEGINNING OF THE EVENTS OF REVELATION, THE LETTERS SENT TO THE 7 STARS AND THE COVENANT Rv3:14-22 (Church in Laodicea) Appearance of Jesus ○1 The Amen: To believe & confess that God's promises will be fulfilled in Christ (2Cor1:20) ○2 The faithful & true witness (Rv1:5) ○3 The ruler of God's creation (Jn1:1-3) → All (spiritual) creation created through Jesus [Lord of lords & King of kings: Jesus/144.000 (Rv17:14). Light (Jesus) Heaven (Tabernacle) Land (New Earth: New saints) Sun Moon Stars (Organization of Gods kingdom) (Gn1:1-5)] \"Lukewarm- neither hot nor cold\" Superficial faith, hypocrites [Yes→ yes, no→ no, anything beyond comes from evil (Mt5:37)] 7 messengers hated Nicolaitans but didn't kick them out Cf. Elijah: Don't waver! Choose God or Baal, not both! (1Ki18:21) \"Spitting you out of Jesus' mouth\"Banishing/kicking them out from the affiliation of Jesus like Adam & Eve Cf. Huge mountain (1st tabernacle) thrown into the sea (world) (Rv8:8) \"Gold refined in fire\" Pure + clean revealed word coming from heaven: Not mixed with worldly doctrines/teachings Poor, wretched, pitiful: Taken over by gentile (→ cannot preach anymore) Blind: Spiritual eye = 7 spirits (Rv5:6) left them \"White clothes to wear\" Righteous acts (Rv19:8) → Fine linen which would be prepared by the bride of Jesus \"Nakedness\" ○1 Committing adultery (sexual immorality) = Associating with Satan (Ez16:36) ○2 Death (2Cor5:1-6) Cf. \"Naked but felt no shame\" (Gn2:24-25) → took off cloth of sin/\"Naked so I hid\" (Gn3:9-10) \"Salve\" Words that 7 spirits (7eyes) would deliver to them [cf. Jn9 & Rv7:17: spring of living water] \"Rebuke & discipline\" God disciplines the ones he loves & accepts as his sons (Heb12:6). Truth=Bitter→ Overcome \"Eat with him\" Jesus will be with us→ can learn & listen (=eat) word of Jesus (Jn14:20, Rom8:9-11) Blessings for OWO \"Sit with Jesus on his throne\" Seat (throne=position of authority) of spirit is flesh (man) [cf. God's throne: Jesus (Mt3:16); Dragon's throne: Beast (Rv13:2)] → Jesus would place his throne on the OWO and reign with him over the world → OWO will rule over all nations with the authority of Jesus in place of Jesus (Mt19:28) 14 \"To the angel of the church in Laodicea write: These are the words of the Amen, the faithful and true witness, the ruler of God's creation. 15 I know your deeds, that you are neither cold nor hot. I wish you were either one or the other! 16 So, because you are lukewarm--neither hot nor cold--I am about to spit you out of my mouth. 17 You say, 'I am rich; I have acquired wealth and do not need a thing.' But you do not realize that you are wretched, pitiful, poor, blind and naked. 18 I counsel you to buy from me gold refined in the fire, so you can become rich; and white clothes to wear, so you can cover your shameful nakedness; and salve to put on your eyes, so you can see. 19 Those whom I love I rebuke and discipline. So be earnest, and repent. 20 Here I am! I stand at the door and knock. If anyone hears my voice and opens the door, I will come in and eat with him, and he with me. 21 To him who overcomes, I will give the right to sit with me on my throne, just as I overcame and sat down with my Father on his throne. 22 He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.\""},{"kind":"notes","page":14,"title":"Notes page 14","text":"What you have seen (Jesus image) What is now (Entity of Satan) What will take place later (Conditional blessings) Main events Ephesus Rev 2:1-7 Holds 7 stars in his right hand & walks among 7 golden lampstands Nicolaitans ○1 Right to eat from the tree of life in paradise - Forsaken first love - Remember the height from which you have fallen - Remove lampstand from its place Smyrna Rv2:8-11 The First and the Last & who died and came to life again Synagogue of Satan ○2 Crown of life ○3 Will not be hurt at all by the second death - Devil will put some of you in prison to test you → suffer persecution for 10 days Pergamum Rv2:12-17 Sharp, double-edged sword Balaam & Balak ○4 Hidden manna ○5 White stone with a new name written on it - Where you live Satan has his throne - Hold teachings of Balaam who taught Balak → Food sacrificed to idols & sexual immorality - Hold teachings of Nicolaitans Thyatira Rv2:18-29 Eyes like blazing fire & feet like burnished bronze Woman Jezebel ○6 Iron scepter ○7 Morning star - Tolerate Jezebel who mislead servants→ sexual immorality & food sacrificed to idols - Cast her on a bed of suffering & strike her children dead - To the rest in Thyatira → hold on to what you have Sardis Rv3:1-6 Holds 7 spirits of God & 7 stars ○8 White clothes ○9 Name will never be blot out from book of life - Come like a thief - A few people in Sardis not soiled their clothes → will walk with Jesus Philadelphia Rv3:7-13 Holy and true & holds the key of David - Synagogue of Satan, who claim to be Jews but are liars - Those who test those who live on the earth ○10 Pillar in temple of God ○11 Name of God, name of Holy city, New Jerusalem, and Jesus new name will be written on him - Placed an open door before you - Keep you from the hour of trial that is going to come upon the whole world to test those who live on the earth - Hold on to what you have so no one will take your crown Laodicea Rv3:14-22 The Amen, the faithful and true witness, the ruler of God's creation ○12 Right to sit with Jesus on Jesus' throne - Lukewarm-neither hot nor cold - Spitting you out of Jesus mouth - Buy gold refined in the fire, white clothes & salve"},{"kind":"notes","page":15,"title":"Notes page 15","text":"REVELATION 4: THE THRONE OF HEAVEN IN THE SPIRITUAL REALM AND ITS ORGANIZATION \"After this\" After John sent letters to 7 messengers in Rv2-3 [6 times: Rv4:1, 7:1, 7:9, 15:5, 18:1, 19:1] \"Door standing open in heaven\" 12 gates in the Holy City New Jerusalem (Rv21:12-21) [John enters through one of 12 gates] \"Voice like a trumpet\" Voice of Jesus (Rv1:10) \"What must take place after\" Events that will happen from Rv4-22 \"One sitting on throne\" God \"Jasper & carnelian\" God is creator of heaven (blue) & earth (red) [→Not about color but about Chin. character!] \"Rainbow resembling emerald\" Covenant (Gn9:11,13,16): God's promise is eternal & steady (Emerald's green color: eternity) The last time is like time of Noah (Mt24:37-39, Lk17:26-30): After flood: Covenant with Noah \"24 thrones & elders\" 24 departments of heaven (Administration) & 24 chief leaders (부장님) \"White clothes\" Righteousness: While carry out their duty → No prejudice & bias, but fair & & true \"Golden crowns\" High & noble position given from God \"Fleshes of lightning\" Rapid movement of spirits (Ez1:14) \"Rumblings & peals of thunder\" Sound of many spirits doing God's work → Shows where God's throne is moving to [cf. Censer=OWO (Rv8:5); God's temple (Rv11:19)] \"7 spirits before God's throne\" Lamps: Enlighten ignorant (Education); Eyes: Monitor & Supervise (Inspection); Planning \"Sea of glass\" Revealed word→ wash hearts & minds with word of life flowing from God's throne (Rv22:1-2) ○1 Moses Time: Bronze Basin made of women's' mirrors (Ex38:8) ○2Solomon Time:'Sea' propped up by 12 cows (12 tribes) (2Chr4:6) ○3Today:OWO (Rv3:12,21) \"4 living creatures\" 4 commander of heavenly armies [Chariot (Ps68), Wind (Zec6), Cherubim (Ez10), Horse (Rv6)] Main Task: Judgment \"Many eyes\" Many spirits (angels) \"6 wings\" 6 divisions of each department → Role of helping 4LC to fulfill God's work Appearance of 4LC Lion (fighting against enemy), Ox (plowing heart of man), Man (distinguish good/evil), Flying Eagle (judge & govern spirits; cf.Ex12: Passover) Cf. Different viewpoint (Ez1) God & his organization will descend to earth (Rv21): Holy City New Jerusalem (made by Jesus&12disciples as foundation)→NHNE → New tabernacle & new saints of the Temple of the Tabernacle of Testimony (Rv15:5, Rv21:1) 1 After this I looked, and there before me was a door standing open in heaven. And the voice I had first heard speaking to me like a trumpet said, \"Come up here, and I will show you what must take place after this.\" 2 At once I was in the Spirit, and there before me was a throne in heaven with someone sitting on it. 3 And the one who sat there had the appearance of jasper and carnelian.A rainbow, resembling an emerald, encircled the throne. 4 Surrounding the throne were twenty-four other thrones, and seated on them were twenty-four elders. They were dressed in white and had crowns of gold on their heads. 5 From the throne came flashes of lightning, rumblings and peals of thunder. Before the throne, seven lamps were blazing. These are the seven spirits of God. 6 Also before the throne there was what looked like a sea of glass, clear as crystal. In the center, around the throne, were four living creatures, and they were covered with eyes, in front and in back. 7 The first living creature was like a lion,the second was like an ox,the third had a face like a man,the fourth was like a flying eagle 8 Each of the four living creatures had six wings and was covered with eyes all around, even under his wings. Day and night they never stop saying: \"Holy, holy, holy is the Lord God Almighty, who was, and is, and is to come.\" 9 Whenever the living creatures give glory, honor and thanks to him who sits on the throne and who lives for ever and ever, 10 the twenty-four elders fall down before him who sits on the throne, and worship him who lives for ever and ever. They lay their crowns before the throne and say: 11 \"You are worthy, our Lord and God, to receive glory and honor and power, for you created all things, an"},{"kind":"notes","page":16,"title":"Notes page 16","text":"REVELATION 5: THE BOOK SEALED WITH SEVEN SEALS \"Scroll sealed with 7 seals\" Book of revelation: Sealed because 7 spirits left 7 messengers→blind (can't understand word) \"Heaven or on earth\" Tabernacle and its saints (congregation members) \"Under the earth\" Abyss = Sea: Worldly church \"Wept and wept\" ○1 No one could receive salvation ○2 Didn't want to go back to sinful world (persecution) ○3 Worried about future life → Cannot give up task of preaching word to whole world Condition to open scroll Overcome ○1 F.C. Overcome the world (Jn16:33) ○2 S.C. Overcome the world again (Rv6:2) \"Lion of tribe of Judah\" Jesus = Lion [King/Head] of tribe of Judah→ Today: Promised pastor = King of tribe of John \"Breaking seals\" Reveal physical entities \"7 horns & 7 spirits\" 7 workers of God newly appointed by Jesus instead of the 7 stars (cf.Rv2:5) [7spirits: cf.Rv4:5] \"Harp\" Bible: O.T. & N.T. (Rv15:2-4) \"Golden bowls\" Heart of man; here: Bowls to contain prayers of saints Order how prayers raised up to God: Many spirits → 4LC → 24 elders → 7 spirits → God \"Full of incense\" Prayers of saints or the requirements of the saints (e.g.: Report inconvenient things upwards) \"New song\" Eternal gospel: Physical fulfillment of N.T. (Rv14:3) \"Kingdom & priests\" 144.000: Those who are sealed with word of God (Rv7:1-8) [cf. GMW: not sealed! (Rv7:14)] \"Many angels\" \"Thousands upon thousands, ten thousand times ten thousand\": Countless (cf.1Sam18:6-8) \"Praise, honor, glory & power\" Because all creation is created according to God's will 1 Then I saw in the right hand of him who sat on the throne a scroll with writing on both sides and sealed with seven seals. 2 And I saw a mighty angel proclaiming in a loud voice, \"Who is worthy to break the seals and open the scroll?\" 3 But no one in heaven or on earth or under the earth could open the scroll or even look inside it. 4 I wept and wept because no one was found who was worthy to open the scroll or look inside. 5 Then one of the elders said to me, \"Do not weep! See, the Lion of the tribe of Judah, the Root of David, has triumphed. He is able to open the scroll and its seven seals.\" 6 Then I saw a Lamb, looking as if it had been slain, standing in the center of the throne, encircled by the four living creatures and the elders. He had seven horns and seven eyes, which are the seven spirits of God sent out into all the earth. 7 He came and took the scroll from the right hand of him who sat on the throne. 8 And when he had taken it, the four living creatures and the twenty-four elders fell down before the Lamb. Each one had a harp and they were holding golden bowls full of incense, which are the prayers of the saints. 9 And they sang a new song: \"You are worthy to take the scroll and to open its seals, because you were slain, and with your blood you purchased men for God from every tribe and language and people and nation. 10 You have made them to be a kingdom and priests to serve our God, and they will reign on the earth.\" 11 Then I looked and heard the voice of many angels, numbering thousands upon thousands, and ten thousand times ten thousand. They encircled the throne and the living creatures and the elders. 12 In a loud voice they sang: \"Worthy is the Lamb, who was slain, to receive power and wealth and wisdom and strength and honor and glory and praise!\" 13 Then I heard every creature in heaven and on earth and under the earth and on the sea, and all that is in them, singing: \"To him who sits on the throne and to the Lamb be praise and honor and glory and power, for ever and ever!\" 14 The four living creatures said, \"Amen,\" and the elders fell down and worshiped."},{"kind":"notes","page":17,"title":"Notes page 17","text":"REVELATION 6: THE END OF SUN, MOON, STARS Horse & its rider Flesh (Is31:3) & spirit (Rv19:11) Horse's color Duty or task Main duty of 4LC Judgment by using gentiles (Is10:5, Dn7, Rv13) Sign of sun, moon, stars One generation (cf.Gn1:14-18): One generation would be (re)created or ended Breaking a seal Prophesied physical reality appears/revealed First Seal \"White horse & its rider\" OWO & Jesus \"Bow (arrow)\" Word of judgment (Hab3:8-9, La2:1-4): Jesus banishes God's chosen people from tabernacle \"Bent on conquest\" Inclined to conquer (overcome) something [F.C. (Jn16:33)/ S.C. Captured beast(Rv19:11,20)] Second Seal \"Red horse given power to\" ○1 Take peace from the earth → conflict ○2 Make men slay each other (Mt24:9-12) \"Large sword\" Word of judgment (Ep6:17): Harsh words which would hurt in their heart (cf. Rv13:3,14) 1 I watched as the Lamb opened the first of the seven seals. Then I heard one of the four living creatures say in a voice like thunder, \"Come!\" 2 I looked, and there before me was a white horse! Its rider held a bow, and he was given a crown, and he rode out as a conqueror bent on conquest. 3 When the Lamb opened the second seal, I heard the second living creature say, \"Come!\" 4 Then another horse came out, a fiery red one. Its rider was given power to take peace from the earth and to make men slay each other. To him was given a large sword. 5 When the Lamb opened the third seal, I heard the third living creature say, \"Come!\" I looked, and there before me was a black horse! Its rider was holding a pair of scales in his hand. 6 Then I heard what sounded like a voice among the four living creatures, saying, \"A quart of wheat for a day's wages, and three quarts of barley for a day's wages, and do not damage the oil and the wine!\" 7 When the Lamb opened the fourth seal, I heard the voice of the fourth living creature say, \"Come!\" 8 I looked, and there before me was a pale horse! Its rider was named Death, and Hades was following close behind him. They were given power over a fourth of the earth to kill by sword, famine and plague, and by the wild beasts of the earth. 9 When he opened the fifth seal, I saw under the altar the souls of those who had been slain because of the word of God and the testimony they had maintained. 10 They called out in a loud voice, \"How long, Sovereign Lord, holy and true, until you judge the inhabitants of the earth and avenge our blood?\" 11 Then each of them was given a white robe, and they were told to wait a little longer, until the number of their fellow servants and brothers who were to be killed as they had been was completed. 12 I watched as he opened the sixth seal. There was a great earthquake. The sun turned black like sackcloth made of goat hair, the whole moon turned blood red, 13 and the stars in the sky fell to earth, as late figs drop from a fig tree when shaken by a strong wind. 14 The sky receded like a scroll, rolling up, and every mountain and island was removed from its place. 15 Then the kings of the earth, the princes, the generals, the rich, the mighty, and every slave and every free man hid in caves and among the rocks of the mountains. 16 They called to the mountains and the rocks, \"Fall on us and hide us from the face of him who sits on the throne and from the wrath of the Lamb! 17 For the great day of their wrath has come, and who can stand?\""},{"kind":"notes","page":18,"title":"Notes page 18","text":"Third Seal \"Black horse & its rider\" \"A pair of scales\" Word that weighs faith & deeds (Prov24:12, 1Sm2:3) \"A quart of wheat & three quarts of barley\" Remnant seeds: A few people saved from first tabernacle (cf. Rv2:24, Rv3:4, Is1:9) \"A day's wages\" One denarius: Word → OWO & remnant seeds testified but only few listened to them \"Not damage oil & wine\" ○1 Oil: Word of testimony of 2 witness (Zech4:11-14, Rv11:3-4) ○2 Wine: Jesus word (Jn15:1) Word is true → Even though they betrayed, God's word shouldn't be eliminated (Mt24:35) Fourth Seal \"Pale horse & its rider\" \"Rider was named Death\" Power to kill the people who betrayed \"Hades following close behind\" Hades = Abyss = Satan's organization: 7 heads & beast with 10 horns (Rv13, Rv17) 4LC brought the beasts to the tabernacle to judge the people who betrayed (Dn7:2-3) Those who are slain would go into Hades → Belong to Satan's side \"Kill a fourth of the earth\" By using gentile pastors 1/4 of the people who betrayed would be killed (cf. Ez14:21) \"Sword\" Satan's doctrine/teaching (Is1:18-20) \"Famine\" Lack of hearing God's word: Gentile overtook tabernacle → No more word from altar (Gn41) \"Plague\" Word of Satan/gentile which spreads like a plague \"Wild beasts\" 7 heads + 10 horns Fifth Seal \"Under the altar\" Place where 4 living creatures are → Spirits of martyrs are under the 4 living creatures \"Souls of who had been slain\" Martyr spirits \"Inhabitants of the earth\" People of tabernacle who betrayed (pastors & congregation) \"White robe\" Kind & comforting words (Zech1:12-13) \"When to avenge their blood\" When 42 months are ended & Babylon is judged with the word of wrath (Rv18:20-24) \"Fellow servants & brothers\" They were also born with God's seed at first, but their death is not 'glorious' but 'shameful' \"When they killed completely\" Within 42 months (Rv11:13) Sixth Seal \"Great earthquake\" Entire organization of tabernacle temple was greatly shaken & deceived by the gentile \"Sun turned black\" Pastors cannot testify word of God anymore \"Sackcloth made of goat hair\" Pastors accepted gentile doctrines as truth [cf. Adam & Eve: Animal skin garment (Gn3:21)] \"Moon turned blood red\" Evangelists accepted word of Satan (=blood of the beast) as truth \"Stars fall from sky to earth\" Congregation members affiliation changed from God's side to Satan's side \"Strong wind\" 4 living creatures brought judgment on the tabernacle at the corners of the earth \"Sky receded like a scroll\" ○1 Spiritual realm (where God, Jesus and many spirits dwell) left the tabernacle ○2 The denomination of the tabernacle changed into Presbyterian denomination \"Every mountain & island removed from its place\" All 80 branch churches → gentile denomination (affiliation) \"Kings, princes, generals, rich, mighty, slave, free man\" Pastors & their congregation members \"Caves, mountains, rocks\" Satan's organization, 7 beasts (Rv17:9), gentile pastors (Dt32:31)"},{"kind":"notes","page":19,"title":"Notes page 19","text":"REVELATION 7: THE CREATION OF THE SEALED 12 TRIBES & THE GREAT MULTITUDE IN WHITE Rv6 versus Rv7 End of first heaven (one generation) versus creation of new heaven (new generation) THE 144.000 WHO ARE SEALED WITH THE WORD OF GOD \"After this\" After sun, moon, stars are darkened and fallen: End of first tabernacle/heaven (Rv6) \"4 angels at corners of the earth\" 4 living creatures (which brought judgment) standing at 4 directions centering tabernacle \"Holding back 4 winds\" 4 living creatures stop judging [Wind: Angel & Judgment] \"Wind prevented to blow\" ○1 Because judgment of tabernacle was finished ○2 In order to seal 144.000 \"Land, sea, any tree\" Tabernacle temple, the world, any denominations or any churchgoers \"Another angel\" Another event \"Coming from the east\" Spiritual east: Place where God's work begins (Ps84:11) cf.Garden Eden. Today:Mt Zion (Rv14) \"Seal of living God\" Word of God (Jn1:1):Promised pastor & 12 tribe leaders become seal & seal (cf.Hag2:23) \"Until put a seal on foreheads of the servants of God\" After 144.000 = firstfruits of Mt Zion (Rv14:1-5) are completely sealed \"12.000 sealed in each tribe\" Names of Jacob's 12 sons to show restoration of 12 tribes of Israel at time of revelation Today: Names of 12 disciples who will reign over 12 tribes (Mt19:28) One of 12 tribes betrayed ○1 O.T. Dan tribe (Gn49:17): Serpent, viper along the path → Manasseh tribe ○2 F.C. Iscariot Judah: Serpent betraying Jesus → Matthias tribe ○3 S.C. Thaddaeus tribe under Shin Jeong-yong (신정용) betrayed on December 1997 1 After this I saw four angels standing at the four corners of the earth, holding back the four winds of the earth to prevent any wind from blowing on the land or on the sea or on any tree. 2 Then I saw another angel coming up from the east, having the seal of the living God. He called out in a loud voice to the four angels who had been given power to harm the land and the sea: 3 \"Do not harm the land or the sea or the trees until we put a seal on the foreheads of the servants of our God.\" 4 Then I heard the number of those who were sealed: 144,000 from all the tribes of Israel. 5 From the tribe of Judah 12,000 were sealed, from the tribe of Reuben 12,000, from the tribe of Gad 12,000, 6 from the tribe of Asher 12,000, from the tribe of Naphtali 12,000, from the tribe of Manasseh 12,000, 7 from the tribe of Simeon 12,000, from the tribe of Levi 12,000, from the tribe of Issachar 12,000, 8 from the tribe of Zebulun 12,000, from the tribe of Joseph 12,000, from the tribe of Benjamin 12,000. 9 After this I looked and there before me was a great multitude that no one could count, from every nation, tribe, people and language, standing before the throne and in front of the Lamb. They were wearing white robes and were holding palm branches in their hands. 10 And they cried out in a loud voice: \"Salvation belongs to our God, who sits on the throne, and to the Lamb.\" 11 All the angels were standing around the throne and around the elders and the four living creatures. They fell down on their faces before the throne and worshiped God, 12 saying: \"Amen! Praise and glory and wisdom and thanks and honor and power and strength be to our God for ever and ever. Amen!\" 13 Then one of the elders asked me, \"These in white robes--who are they, and where did they come from?\" 14 I answered, \"Sir, you know.\" And he said, \"These are they who have come out of the great tribulation; they have washed their robes and made them white in the blood of the Lamb. 15 Therefore, \"they are before the throne of God and serve him day and night in his temple; and he who sits on the throne will spread his tent over them. 16 Never again will they hunger; never again will they thirst. The sun will not beat upon them, nor any scorching heat. 17 For the Lamb at the center of the throne will be their shepherd; he will lead them to springs of living water. And God will wipe away every tear from their eyes.\""},{"kind":"notes","page":20,"title":"Notes page 20","text":"THE CREATION OF THE GREAT MULTITUDE IN WHITE \"After this\" After 144.000 are sealed \"Great multitude no one could count\" Who have washed their robes and made them white in the blood of the Lamb \"Nation, tribe, people, language\" Church, denomination, congregation, doctrine → Sea under Babylon (Rv17:15, Rv18:4) [Appears 7 times: Rv5:9, Rv7:9, Rv10:11, Rv11:9, Rv13:7, Rv14:6, Rv17:15] \"White robes\" To wash their robes and make them white in the blood of the Lamb (Rv7:14) \"Palm branches\" They will give glory, honor, and praise to God and Jesus (as Israelites welcomed Jesus) \"Salvation belongs to God\" Salvation can only be received where God & Jesus is → Mt. Zion \"Great tribulation\" Great Judgment: After 144.000 are sealed, 4LC would release winds to blow again to the sea \"Washed their robes\" At the sea of glass = missionary center \"Sun & scorching heat\" False pastor & false doctrine which kills people's spirit (Rv16:8, Mt13:6) \"Spring of living water\" Pastor with the word of life: Jesus leads us to promised pastor who has word of life (Rv22:17) Siloam=spring: Jesus (shepherd) gives salve/word (salvia+mud)→us (blind man) (Jn9, Ez47) 12 Disciples 12 Sons of Jacob 12 Precious Stones (Rv21) 1 John Judah Emerald 녹보석 2 Peter Joseph Jasper 벽석 3 James Reuben Sapphire 남보석 4 Andrew Gad Chalcedony 옥수 5 Thaddaeus Asher Sardonyx 홍마노 6 Phillip Naphtali Carnelian 홍보석 7 Simon Simeon Chrysolite 황옥 8 Bartholomew Zebulun Beryl 녹옥 9 Matthew Levi Topaz 담황옥 10 Matthias Manasseh Chrysoprase 비취옥 11 James Issachar Jacinth 청옥 12 Thomas Benjamin Amethyst 자정"},{"kind":"notes","page":21,"title":"Notes page 21","text":"REVELATION 8: THE SOUND OF THE SEVEN TRUMPETS AND THE EVENTS WHICH THEY PROCLAIM Rv6 versus Rv8 Before 42 months versus during 42 months \"Silence in heaven\" ○1 Spiritual realm: Judgment on tabernacle ended ○2 Tabernacle: Overtaken by gentile → gentile's possession War (great uproar) over when one side won over the other → silence [cf. \"whole world at rest & peace\": overtaken by gentile (Zec1:10-11)] \"About half an hour\" Vision: 30 minutes long / Reality: 6 months (1980.September 14 - 1981 March 14) \"Seven trumpets\" Spirit (trumpeter) use flesh (trumpet) who will preach word of testimony (sound of trumpet) ○1 To announce destruction of chosen people (Is18:3, Is58:1, Is1:18-20) ○2 To announce how they are being killed (= events occurring when seals are opened) \"Golden censer\" OWO = promised pastor (Lk12:49) Moses time: In holy place / F.C.: In most holy place → curtain: Jesus body (Heb10:19-20) ○1 New tabernacle would be established with the appearance of the golden censer ○2 One tabernacle should be divided (separated) into two [2nd day event (Gn1:6-8)] Promised pastor out of prison (1981.2.2.) → Started worship service (1981.3.14.): 3years From that time the 2nd tabernacle would be separated from 1st tabernacle \"Earth on which fire hurled down\" Tabernacle temple which betrayed WATER UNDER THE SKY (HEAVEN) WATER ABOVE THE SKY (HEAVEN) OLD (FIRST) TABERNACLE NEW (SECOND) TABERNACLE (SSN+REMNANT SEED) WORLDLY WORD REVEALED WORD SEA SEA OF GLASS [Cf. 3rd day event (Gn1:9-13): Land (Temple of Tabernacle of Testimony) finally revealed to the world (1984.3.14)] 1 When he opened the seventh seal, there was silence in heaven for about half an hour. 2 And I saw the seven angels who stand before God, and to them were given seven trumpets. 3 Another angel, who had a golden censer, came and stood at the altar. He was given much incense to offer, with the prayers of all the saints, on the golden altar before the throne. 4 The smoke of the incense, together with the prayers of the saints, went up before God from the angel's hand. 5 Then the angel took the censer, filled it with fire from the altar, and hurled it on the earth; and there came peals of thunder, rumblings, flashes of lightning and an earthquake. 6 Then the seven angels who had the seven trumpets prepared to sound them. 7 The first angel sounded his trumpet, and there came hail and fire mixed with blood, and it was hurled down upon the earth. A third of the earth was burned up, a third of the trees were burned up, and all the green grass was burned up. 8 The second angel sounded his trumpet, and something like a huge mountain, all ablaze, was thrown into the sea. A third of the sea turned into blood, 9 a third of the living creatures in the sea died, and a third of the ships were destroyed. 10 The third angel sounded his trumpet, and a great star, blazing like a torch, fell from the sky on a third of the rivers and on the springs of water-- 11 the name of the star is Wormwood. A third of the waters turned bitter, and many people died from the waters that had become bitter. 12 The fourth angel sounded his trumpet, and a third of the sun was struck, a third of the moon, and a third of the stars, so that a third of them turned dark. A third of the day was without light, and also a third of the night. 13 As I watched, I heard an eagle that was flying in midair call out in a loud voice: \"Woe! Woe! Woe to the inhabitants of the earth, because of the trumpet blasts about to be sounded by the other three angels!\""},{"kind":"notes","page":22,"title":"Notes page 22","text":"First Trumpet → Land \"Hail & fire\" Word of wrath (Is28:2, Rv16:21) & word of judgment \"Mixed with blood\" Symbolizing the word that Jesus delivered even by shedding his blood \"1/3 of earth\" 1/3 of the tabernacle \"1/3 of trees\" 1/3 of pastors (=denominations) \"All green grass\" All congregation members of the tabernacle Second Trumpet → Sea \"Something like huge mountain\" Headquarter church of tabernacle \"Being thrown into sea\" Tabernacle was thrown into world → gentile denomination \"1/3 of sea turned blood\" 1/3 of tabernacle's doctrine mixed with gentile doctrine → dead doctrine (blood of the dead) cf. Choice wine (word of God) + water (sea=gentile doctrine) → dead (Is2:22) \"1/3 of living creatures died\" 1/3 of congregation members died spiritually \"1/3 of ships destroyed\" 1/3 of branch churches of tabernacle became gentile denominations Third Trumpet → Rivers & springs \"Great star\" One who belonged to tabernacle, but later became one with gentile to destroy tabernacle Nicolas, Balaam: Pastor Oh \"Wormwood\" 'Bitterness': False doctrine like bitter waters →kills spirit [cf. poison of cobras (Dt32:32-33)] \"1/3 of rivers & springs\" 1/3 of false evangelists & false pastors (Pastor Oh would teach them with bitter water) Fourth Trumpet → Sun, moon, stars \"1/3 of sun, moon, stars\" 1/3 of pastors, evangelists, congregation members \"Being struck & turned dark\" Being attacked and defeated by the gentile & cannot testify word of truth anymore \"1/3 of day & night\" Day: Those who have the word of light (Jn1:1-4) Night: Those who don't have the word of light (1Thes5:1-5) → As sun, moon, stars lost their light (word) they could not reign over anything anymore [One who governs day: Sun / One who governs night: Moon & Stars (Gn1:14-18)] \"Eagle flying in midair\" 4 living creatures in tabernacle temple (Rv13) [cf. carcass=dead bodies & vultures=4LC (Mt24:28)] \"Woe, woe, woe\" Woe (=plague) of 5th (Rv9:1-12), 6th (Rv9:13-21), 7th trumpet (Rv11:15-18)"},{"kind":"notes","page":23,"title":"Notes page 23","text":"REVELATION 9: THE MESSENGERS FROM THE ABYSS AND DEATH Rv8 versus Rv9 Inner destroyer judging versus inner destroyer bringing outer destroyer to judge betrayers Fifth Trumpet \"Star fallen from sky\" Wormwood: Balaam, Nicolas (Rv8:10-11) \"Given key of the Abyss\" Jesus gave him authority to rule over tab. for a while so that betrayers will be completely destroyed Even though Oh was banished from tabernacle due to conflict with evangelists, he returned with power & authority to rule tabernacle again from May 1981 → Devoured tabernacle aggressively \"Smoke from Abyss\" Ecclesiastical authority (Pastor Oh took authority from the gentile) \"Sun & sky darkened\" Pastor & congregation could not testify God's word anymore because smoke prevented them doing so \"Locusts out of Abyss\" Organization of Satan = Nicolaitans = 7+10 beasts cf. Locusts swarm, great locusts, young locusts, other locusts (Jo1:4-6), Gold, silver, bronze, iron (Dn2), 4 beasts (Dn7) → Different denominations come together & become one → Mixed teachings \"Power like scorpions\" Having power like poison of cobra to kill people's spirits \"Grass, plant, tree of earth\" Churchgoers or denominations of the world 1 The fifth angel sounded his trumpet, and I saw a star that had fallen from the sky to the earth. The star was given the key to the shaft of the Abyss. 2 When he opened the Abyss, smoke rose from it like the smoke from a gigantic furnace. The sun and sky were darkened by the smoke from the Abyss. 3 And out of the smoke locusts came down upon the earth and were given power like that of scorpions of the earth. 4 They were told not to harm the grass of the earth or any plant or tree, but only those people who did not have the seal of God on their foreheads. 5 They were not given power to kill them, but only to torture them for five months. And the agony they suffered was like that of the sting of a scorpion when it strikes a man. 6 During those days men will seek death, but will not find it; they will long to die, but death will elude them. 7 The locusts looked like horses prepared for battle. On their heads they wore something like crowns of gold, and their faces resembled human faces. 8 Their hair was like women's hair, and their teeth were like lions' teeth. 9 They had breastplates like breastplates of iron, and the sound of their wings was like the thundering of many horses and chariots rushing into battle. 10 They had tails and stings like scorpions, and in their tails they had power to torment people for five months. 11 They had as king over them the angel of the Abyss, whose name in Hebrew is Abaddon, and in Greek, Apollyon. 12 The first woe is past; two other woes are yet to come. 13 The sixth angel sounded his trumpet, and I heard a voice coming from the horns of the golden altar that is before God. 14 It said to the sixth angel who had the trumpet, \"Release the four angels who are bound at the great river Euphrates.\" 15 And the four angels who had been kept ready for this very hour and day and month and year were released to kill a third of mankind. 16 The number of the mounted troops was two hundred million. I heard their number. 17 The horses and riders I saw in my vision looked like this: Their breastplates were fiery red, dark blue, and yellow as sulfur. The heads of the horses resembled the heads of lions, and out of their mouths came fire, smoke and sulfur. 18 A third of mankind was killed by the three plagues of fire, smoke and sulfur that came out of their mouths. 19 The power of the horses was in their mouths and in their tails; for their tails were like snakes, having heads with which they inflict injury. 20 The rest of mankind that were not killed by these plagues still did not repent of the work of their hands; they did not stop worshiping demons, and idols of gold, silver, bronze, stone and wood--idols that cannot see or hear or walk. 21 Nor did they repent of their murders, their magic arts, their sexual immorality or their thefts."},{"kind":"notes","page":24,"title":"Notes page 24","text":"\"Not to be harmed\" Because the judgment on the tabernacle was not yet finished (cf.Ez9:1-6) \"Torture for 5 months\" 150 days (1981 May-September): Like time of Noah (Gn7:24) Gentile doctrines (many waters) flood tabernacle for 150 days→ forced to listen to gentile doctrines \"Agony like scorpion sting\" Chosen people were tormented by forcefully listen to gentile doctrines \"Death will elude them\" Cannot leave tabernacle temple Appearance of locusts \"Horses prepared for battle\" Armies (flesh) prepared for spiritual war (battle) \"Something like crowns of gold\" Positions of authority made by their own, not given from God \"Faces like human faces\" They are beasts but masquerade image of human to deceive people (2Cor11:13-15, Mt7:15) \"Like women's hair\" Pastors (Gn2, Gal4:19) of big denominations that have lots of congregation members \"Breastplates of iron\" Being armed with gentile doctrines as strong as iron \"Lion's teeth\" False doctrine/teachings which kill sheep-like believers \"Sound of wings like thundering of many horses & chariots\" As God has his own armies & divisions (Rv4: 4LC,6wings), so does Satan (Rv9:16) → rushing into battle to fight against God's armies \"Tails & stings like scorpions\" False prophets (Is9:15) & false doctrines like poison of scorpions to kill people's spirits \"Angel of the Abyss\" \"Abaddon/Apollyon\"= Destroyer: Great prostitute (Rv17): To reign over organization of 7+10 beasts Sixth trumpet \"Horns of golden altar\" 4 spirits which have authority to lead service in spiritual realm \"Voice\" To announce that coming event would take place during service time \"4 angels\" Sinned angels (2Pt2:4): Bound at dungeon until judgment time because they sinned against God 유재열, 오평호, 탁성환, 김정두 \"Great river Euphrates\" 1 of 4 rivers in Garden of Eden → To show that event like time of Adam ○1 4 rivers: 4LC ○2 Euphrates: Dwelling place of evil spirits or place from which evil spirits come out \"Hour, day, month, year\" 2pm, Sept 20 1981: 1/3 of tabernacle people receive mark of beast & worship idols→gentile possession \"Number of mounted troops: Two hundred million\" Uncountable number \"Horses & riders\" Flesh & evil spirits \"Breastplates: Fiery red, dark blue, yellow as sulfur\" Armed with various kinds of gentile doctrines \"Heads like lions\" Like fierce lions to devour sheep-like believers \"Fire, smoke, sulfur out from their mouths\" Gentile doctrines that kill people's spirits \"Power of horses in their mouths & tails\" \"Tails like snakes\" False pastor (prophet): 17 evangelists, later set up as idols (Rv13:15) Become one with gentile & stood on Satan's side \"Tail's heads\" 7 heads (Rv17:9): 7 gentile pastors (7hills/7kings) → They would set up the tails as idols \"Rest of mankind not repenting their sins & worshipping demons and idols\" ○1 Demons: 7 heads ○2 Idols: Tails (Rv13:15-16) Prove of their betrayal (Rv9:21) \"Murders\" Being handed over to gentile to be put to death \"Magic arts\" False omens & false revelations \"Sexual immorality\" Receiving word of Satan & associating with Satan's spirit \"Thefts\" Becoming companions of thieves (Is1:23)"},{"kind":"notes","page":25,"title":"Notes page 25","text":"REVELATION 10: THE OPEN WORD FROM HEAVEN AND THE MYSTERY OF THE SEVENTH TRUMPET \"Another mighty angel\" Spirit of truth = Counselor spirit = Angel speaking on behalf of Jesus (Jn14:26, Rv15:26, Rv16:13-15) Another angel: Not angel who was previously blowing trumpet \"Robed in a cloud\" Govern (rule over) many spirits & comes down to earth with them \"Rainbow above head\" Covenant → \"promised angel\" = Counselor [cf. time of Noah (Gn9:16)] \"Face like sun\" Appearance of Jesus (Rv1:16) \"Legs like fiery pillars\" Appearance of God (Ez1:26-28) → Angel who brings the word of God & Jesus with him \"Little scroll\" Book of revelation: Little because it doesn't refer to whole Bible \"Right foot on sea\" 7+10 = Babylon: Organization of Satan (Rv17:3, 15) \"Left foot on land\" Tabernacle temple which betrayed (Rv13) \"Plant\" (=Trample) Judge betrayers & destroyers with open scroll \"7 thunders\" 7 spirits before God's throne \"Not write it down\" Open scroll would be given to John who would swallow it up \"Mystery of 7th trumpet\" Secret of eternal life & salvation (resurrection) ○1 Physical dead come to life again as spiritual body ○2 Living beings being changed = transfigured (1Cor15:51-54) Mortal/Perishable (flesh) → Immortal/Imperishable (spirit) [transfigured like Jesus] ○3 Kingdom of the world has become the kingdom of God (7th trumpet starts blowing: Rv11:15) Condition: Woman sent by heaven (7th trumpet: F.C.Jesus/S.C.OWO) giving yeast to people (Mt13:33) \"Sweet in mouth, sour in stomach\" Realizing God's word felt amazing, but difficult to preach word to rebellious people \"Prophecy\" To speak about the future event on behalf of someone \"People, nations, languages, kings\" Pastors & congregation belonging to gentile & all churches & pastors in the world (Ez3) At first John would prophesy to tabernacle, later also preach word to churches of the world! Kings, rulers (worldly pastors) kiss son (learn word from him) with fear (authority to judge) (Ps2:9-12) 1 Then I saw another mighty angel coming down from heaven. He was robed in a cloud, with a rainbow above his head; his face was like the sun, and his legs were like fiery pillars. 2 He was holding a little scroll, which lay open in his hand. He planted his right foot on the sea and his left foot on the land, 3 and he gave a loud shout like the roar of a lion. When he shouted, the voices of the seven thunders spoke. 4 And when the seven thunders spoke, I was about to write; but I heard a voice from heaven say, \"Seal up what the seven thunders have said and do not write it down.\" 5 Then the angel I had seen standing on the sea and on the land raised his right hand to heaven. 6 And he swore by him who lives for ever and ever, who created the heavens and all that is in them, the earth and all that is in it, and the sea and all that is in it, and said, \"There will be no more delay! 7 But in the days when the seventh angel is about to sound his trumpet, the mystery of God will be accomplished, just as he announced to his servants the prophets.\" 8 Then the voice that I had heard from heaven spoke to me once more: \"Go, take the scroll that lies open in the hand of the angel who is standing on the sea and on the land.\" 9 So I went to the angel and asked him to give me the little scroll. He said to me, \"Take it and eat it. It will turn your stomach sour, but in your mouth it will be as sweet as honey.\" 10 I took the little scroll from the angel's hand and ate it. It tasted as sweet as honey in my mouth, but when I had eaten it, my stomach turned sour. 11 Then I was told, \"You must prophesy again about many peoples, nations, languages and kings.\""},{"kind":"notes","page":26,"title":"Notes page 26","text":"REVELATION 4 THE THRONE OF HEAVEN IN THE SPIRITUAL REALM AND ITS ORGANIZATION 1-2 Door standing open in heaven 3 Appearance of throne of God 4 Appearance of 24 thrones of 24 elders 5 Flash of lightning, rumblings, peals of thunder & the seven spirits before throne of God 6-8 Sea of glass & 4 living creatures & their appearance 9-11 Give all the glory and honor to God and Jesus REVELATION 5 THE BOOK SEALED WITH SEVEN SEALS 1-5 Scroll sealed with 7 seals 6-8 Seven horns, golden bowls, prayers of saints 9-10 Kingdom and priests purchased with the blood of Jesus 11-14 Number of many angels & to God be praise, honor, glory, and power REVELATION 6 THE END OF SUN, MOON, STARS 1-8 Events of 1st→4th seal: Judgment on the tabernacle temple through Jesus and four living creatures 9-11 Event of the 5th seal: Souls of martyr spirits 12-17 Event of the 6th seal: Fall of sun, moon, stars REVELATION 7 THE CREATION OF THE SEALED 12 TRIBES & THE GREAT MULTITUDE IN WHITE 1-8 144.000 who are sealed with the word of God 9-17 Creation of the great multitude in white REVELATION 8 THE SOUND OF THE SEVEN TRUMPETS AND THE EVENTS WHICH THEY PROCLAIM 1-5 7th seal & golden censer & the prayers of the saints 6-13 Events of 1st→4th trumpet (land, sea, rivers & springs, sun, moon, stars) REVELATION 9 THE MESSENGERS FROM THE ABYSS AND DEATH 1-6 Events of the 5th trumpet: Locusts coming out of Abyss & 150 day torture 7-12 Events of the 5th trumpet: Appearance of the locusts & the angel of the Abyss 13-21 Events of 6th trumpet (4 angels kept ready for very hour, day, month, year) REVELATION 10 THE OPEN WORD FROM HEAVEN AND THE MYSTERY OF THE SEVENTH TRUMPET 1-7 A mighty angel & the open scroll 8-11 Swallowing the open scroll & John's duty REVELATION 11 TWO WITNESSES AND THE SEVENTH TRUMPET 1-6 Two witnesses 7-14 Death & resurrection of two witnesses 15-19 7th trumpet & God's temple opened"},{"kind":"notes","page":27,"title":"Notes page 27","text":"REVELATION 11: TWO WITNESSES AND THE SEVENTH TRUMPET \"Reed like measuring rod\" Reed: Tool used for measuring something like a ruler Rod: Staff that we can rely on (lean against) Rod: ○1 Word (Rv10) ○2 Person with word (Rv11) ○3 Iron scepter (Rv2) → One who plays role as helper to measure something, but has weak faith like a reed 홍종효 (one of 2 witnesses): Kicked out of SCJ 1987 because he set up idol (cf. Aaron's calf image) \"Do not measure\" Not giving them the word \"Outer court\" Tabernacle temple (already given to gentile) \"Holy city\" Because Jesus had been there before, but now tabernacle (=heaven) was separated into 2 (Rv8:3-5) \"Prophecy for 1260 days\" Period after John received open scroll and was commanded to measure temple: No exact time frame ○1 Period of destruction: 1260 days (1980.9.14-1984.3.14) ○2 Woman→ desert: 1260 days (1980.10.-1984.4) ○3 Period of prophesying: No exact start/end point \"Clothed in sackcloth\" Have word of repentance for dead people (Rv8/9: 1/3, 1/3, 1/3) to waken up their dead deeds \"2 olive trees\" 2 witnesses that have word of testimony (Zec4:11-14) [cf. oil (Mt25)] \"2 lampstands\" Role to enlighten the ignorant people with word of God \"Fire from their mouth\" Word of judgment \"Enemies\" Evil spirits = Satan's doctrine/word (Rv16:13-14) 1 I was given a reed like a measuring rod and was told, \"Go and measure the temple of God and the altar, and count the worshipers there. 2 But exclude the outer court; do not measure it, because it has been given to the Gentiles. They will trample on the holy city for 42 months. 3 And I will give power to my two witnesses, and they will prophesy for 1,260 days, clothed in sackcloth.\" 4 These are the two olive trees and the two lampstands that stand before the Lord of the earth. 5 If anyone tries to harm them,fire comes from their mouths and devours their enemies.This is how anyone who wants to harm them must die 6 These men have power to shut up the sky so that it will not rain during the time they are prophesying; and they have power to turn the waters into blood and to strike the earth with every kind of plague as often as they want. 7 Now when they have finished their testimony, the beast that comes up from the Abyss will attack them, and overpower and kill them. 8 Their bodies will lie in the street of the great city, which is figuratively called Sodom and Egypt, where also their Lord was crucified. 9 For three and a half days men from every people, tribe, language and nation will gaze on their bodies and refuse them burial. 10 The inhabitants of the earth will gloat over them and will celebrate by sending each other gifts, because these two prophets had tormented those who live on the earth. 11 But after the 3 and a half days a breath of life from God entered them,and they stood on their feet,and terror struck those who saw them. 12 Then they heard a loud voice from heaven saying to them, \"Come up here.\" And they went up to heaven in a cloud, while their enemies looked on. 13 At that very hour there was a severe earthquake and a tenth of the city collapsed. Seven thousand people were killed in the earthquake, and the survivors were terrified and gave glory to the God of heaven. 14 The second woe has passed; the third woe is coming soon. 15 The seventh angel sounded his trumpet, and there were loud voices in heaven, which said: \"The kingdom of the world has become the kingdom of our Lord and of his Christ, and he will reign for ever and ever.\" 16 And the twenty-four elders, who were seated on their thrones before God, fell on their faces and worshiped God, 17 saying: \"We give thanks to you, Lord God Almighty, the One who is and who was, because you have taken your great power and have begun to reign. 18 The nations were angry; and your wrath has come. The time has come for judging the dead, and for rewarding your servants the prophets and your saints and those who reverence your name, both small and great--and for destroying those who destroy the earth.\" 19 Then"},{"kind":"notes","page":28,"title":"Notes page 28","text":"\"Shut up sky\" Prevent the sky (=cloud: Who have God's word of testimony) from preaching word to betrayer (Mt7:6) \"Turn waters into blood\" Revealing doctrines of destroyers (waters) as untruth → unable to drink \"Finish their testimony\" They revealed entity of betrayers and destroyers publicly [Testimony: What has already been fulfilled] \"Beast attack them\" Wormwood: Mr Oh suggested to talk to 2 witnesses, but at meeting place (coffee shop in front of Jung-bu police station) policemen arrested them for defamation of character \"Kill them\" Death of their duty (task): Not testify about God's word anymore \"Bodies lie in street of great city\" Tabernacle temple: After 2 witnesses were released from prison, they would go to tabernacle, but they could not testify word anymore because of worldly law \"Sodom, Egypt, where Jesus was crucified (Golgotha)\" ○1 Sodom (Is1:2,10, Gn19): Like time of Lot ○2 Egypt (Ex7-12): Like time of Moses ○3 Golgotha = Jerusalem: Tabernacle \"Men from every people, tribe, language, nation\" Congregation belonging to destroyers, including tabernacle people \"Refuse them burial\" They refused to admit them into their own denomination (=tomb/grave: place where dead are buried) \"Sending gifts\" They exchanged pleasant words (Jn4:19) because 2 witnesses could not testify word to them anymore \"Three and half days\" 1981.1.30. - 1981.2.2: After being in prison for 98 days, released by receiving suspended sentence \"Breath of life\" Word of life (Jn1:1-4): Duty they had lost would be restored → Testify word again \"Went up to heaven\" First heaven=Tabernacle temple: Went to tabern. with their brothers (clouds) who have God's word \"In a cloud\" Riding a cloud: Being led by the holy spirit (Ex19:3) ○1 Cloud: Many spirits/angels (Ps104:3, Heb1:7, Ps68:17) ○2 Cloud: Who have God's word (rain) \"Severe earthquake\" Hearts of tabernacle people greatly shaken because their doctrines were revealed as untruth on account of their testimony (Between 1982-1983: A lot of spiritual war) \"1/10 of city collapsed\" 1/10 of the organization of tabernacle was destroyed = came to God's side [One of 10 horns=elders (La Byung-jun) would come to SCJ) \"7.000 killed\" Number of all congregation members of tabernacle → Tabernacle temple would no longer exist! [Either it was destroyed into God's side or into Satan's side: Temple+80 branch churches passed away] \"Survivors\" Those who fled from tabernacle to Mt. Zion (cf.Mt24) (Those victorious over the beast, his image, and number of his name & gather beside the sea of glass) \"Mystery of 7th trumpet\" Salvation & eternal life (Rv10:7) ○1 Physical dead → Come to life again as spiritual body ○2 Physically living → transfigured [Perishable clothed with (being one with/united with) imperishable, mortal clothed with immortal] ○2 Kingdom of the world → kingdom of God (God begins to reign over all nations) \"God's temple in heaven opened\" Way to make people enter temple of God (Temple of Tabernacle of Testimony) was opened Betrayer & destroyer were not allowed to enter God's kingdom without receiving God's wrath (Rv16) \"Ark of the covenant\" Word of New Testament To show that this temple is the promised temple that was prophesied in New Testament \"A great hailstorm\" Promised pastor who has word of wrath: Poured out in Rv16,17,18 [cf. hailstones (Rv16:21)] ⋆ 1984 September 24 On that day 1984.3.14 was declared as foundation date of God's kingdom (Hag2:10-19) From that day on, people can receive blessings from God!"},{"kind":"notes","page":29,"title":"Notes page 29","text":"REVELATION 12: THE VICTORY OF THE CHILD WHO WILL RULE OVER ALL NATIONS Importance of Rv12 3 entities (betrayers, destroyer, savior) appear in same place 3 wondrous signs ○1 Woman clothed with sun, moon, stars give birth to male child who will rule over all nations ○2 Red dragon who has 7 heads and 10 horns comes up to heaven and hurl 1/3 of stars down to earth ○3 7 angels come out from heaven with 7 bowls full of God's wrath Rv13 before Rv12 Rv13: 1st war (Dragon versus those who live in heaven = tabernacle people) Rv12: 2nd war (Michael + angels / Male child + brothers versus dragon + angels / 7+10) \"Great & wondrous sign\" Male child who will rule over all nations with iron scepter born from woman (\"in heaven\": tabernacle) → Unbelievable that savior comes from cult denomination! \"Woman dressed with Sun: God-Father (Ps84:11) Moon: Jesus-Mother (Gal4:26) 12 stars: 12 disciples-sons (Gn37:9-11) sun, moon, 12 stars\" →Once, spiritual realm descended upon/was with her, but after betrayal, sky receded like scroll (Rv6) \"Being pregnant\" Woman was pastor who had her own congregation members: Ryu Jae-yeol (Mt24:19) 1 A great and wondrous sign appeared in heaven: a woman clothed with the sun, with the moon under her feet and a crown of twelve stars on her head. 2 She was pregnant and cried out in pain as she was about to give birth. 3 Then another sign appeared in heaven: an enormous red dragon with seven heads and ten horns and seven crowns on his heads. 4 His tail swept a third of the stars out of the sky and flung them to the earth. The dragon stood in front of the woman who was about to give birth, so that he might devour her child the moment it was born. 5 She gave birth to a son, a male child, who will rule all the nations with an iron scepter. And her child was snatched up to God and to his throne. 6 The woman fled into the desert to a place prepared for her by God, where she might be taken care of for 1,260 days. 7 And there was war in heaven. Michael and his angels fought against the dragon, and the dragon and his angels fought back. 8 But he was not strong enough, and they lost their place in heaven. 9 The great dragon was hurled down--that ancient serpent called the devil, or Satan, who leads the whole world astray. He was hurled to the earth, and his angels with him. 10 Then I heard a loud voice in heaven say: \"Now have come the salvation and the power and the kingdom of our God, and the authority of his Christ. For the accuser of our brothers, who accuses them before our God day and night, has been hurled down. 11 They overcame him by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of their testimony; they did not love their lives so much as to shrink from death. 12 Therefore rejoice, you heavens and you who dwell in them! But woe to the earth and the sea, because the devil has gone down to you! He is filled with fury, because he knows that his time is short.\" 13 When the dragon saw that he had been hurled to the earth, he pursued the woman who had given birth to the male child. 14 The woman was given the two wings of a great eagle, so that she might fly to the place prepared for her in the desert, where she would be taken care of for a time, times and half a time, out of the serpent's reach. 15 Then from his mouth the serpent spewed water like a river, to overtake the woman and sweep her away with the torrent. 16 But the earth helped the woman by opening its mouth and swallowing the river that the dragon had spewed out of his mouth. 17 Then the dragon was enraged at the woman and went off to make war against the rest of her offspring--those who obey God's commandments and hold to the testimony of Jesus."},{"kind":"notes","page":30,"title":"Notes page 30","text":"\"Crying out in pain\" She (Mr Ryu) could not overcome present situation of tabernacle & knew that her sons & daughters (congregation) would be devoured by gentile, but because she already lost power & authority to rule tabernacle, there was nothing she could do. \"About to give birth\" Her duty was about to end when male child is born → flee into desert to place prepared for her \"Another sign\" Dragon with 7 heads & 10 horns would go up to heaven & flung 1/3 of stars down to earth with his tail (cf. 6th trumpet event) \"7 heads\" 7 hills = 7 mountains = 7 churches (denomination): 7 pastors who have their own churches (Rv17:9) 7 kings = 7 pastors coming up from the sea which is the world \"10 horns\" 10 kings = 10 elders without their own churches, but authority to rule for a while with beast (Rv17:12) \"Tail\" False prophets (pastors): Once, they were evangelists of tabernacle, but have been appointed as pastors by Presbyterian law (1981.9.20)→ gentile pastors (idols: Rv13) to destroy the tabernacle \"Dragon try devour child\" Instead of dragon who has been ruling before, male child will get authority to rule over all nations → Dragon tried to devour (= take to his side) the male child (cf.Mt4) \"Child snatched up to God & his throne\" Place where God & his throne are: Mt Zion (Rv14/15) Cf. Jesus being tested by the devil: Stones changed into bread (Mt4): Stones (gentile pastors) & bread (God's pastors) → Satan's pastors changed into God's pastors Pastor Ryu laid hand on Mr Tak & Mr Kim (1981.9.20) → Satan's pastors (stones) stand on altar of tabernacle as if they are God's pastors:Try to deceive tabernacle people to worship Satan & his pastors From that time, male child would not unite with gentile but separate himself & fight against them with \"blood of Jesus\" & \"word of testimony\" (=weapon with which he fight against dragon) \"Woman fled to desert\" Sea = many waters = place without word = place where wild beasts dwell: U.S. (theology school) 2nd trip to desert after he came back to tabernacle for a while! (1260 days: 1980.10.-1984.4.) \"Now, salvation & power & kingdom of God have come\" After fighting & overcoming dragon and his angels \"Heavens will rejoice\" Those who gather into the temple of the tabernacle of testimony \"Woe to earth & sea\" Plagues to tabernacle & world (churches belonging to destroyers) → Since dragon was defeated & hurled down to earth, his anger would pour out on churches including tabernacle → they would refuse to repent of their sins and listen to God's word (Rv16:8-9) \"Dragon pursued woman\" At first tabernacle was treated as a cult, after gentile had overtaken it was regarded as 'orthodox', but when dragon was kicked out, tabernacle would again suffer persecutions from gentile as a cult! \"Woman given 2 wings of great eagle\" Would leave for desert with help of 4 living creatures [cf. Pastor Oh (Zec5:5-9)] \" A time, times and half a time\" 3 1/2 years = 42 months (Dn11:13) \"Out of serpent's reach\" Out of serpent's influence: She fled to avoid serpent's interference & persecution Rv12:13 versus Rv12:14 After 42m ended (after dragon was hurled down) versus within 42m (while dragon was in tabernacle) \"Water like a river\" Pastor Oh spoke many slanderous words about Mr Ryu while he was absent from tabernacle \"Overtake her & sweep her away with torrent\" By talking bad behind his back he tried to get rid of Mr Ryu \"Earth helped woman by opening its mouth & swallowing river\" Congregation withstood from bad words and curses the serpent spewed about Mr Ryu and kept their heart toward him \"Rest of her offspring- those who obey God's commandments and hold to the testimony of Jesus\" Remnant seed (Rv6:6); male child & his brothers (Rv12:11); Those who are victorious over beast & gather in front of sea of glass (Rv15:2); 144.000 standing on Mt. Zion with Jesus (Rv14:1) \"Dragon stood on shore of the sea\" Congregation who belong to dragon (worldly churches) [Shore on the sea = sand on the sea] To make worldly kings gather in one place "},{"kind":"notes","page":31,"title":"Notes page 31","text":"REVELATION 13: THE CHOSEN PEOPLE WHO BETRAYED & RECEIVED THE MARK OF THE BEAST Beast coming out of sea \"Sea\" Religious world which Satan has been reigning over until now (Dn7:2-3, Dn7:17) \"7 heads & 10 horns with 10 crowns\" 10 horns receive authority from 7 heads (anointed as 10 elders by Presbyterian law) 7 heads: 7 hills= 7 kings → 7 pastors (Rv17:9) 10 horns: 10 kings→ 10 pastors (Rv17:12) \"Each head blasphemous name\" Self-made title/position of authority (in order to devour the tabernacle) \"Resembled leopard, bear, lion\" Destroyers expressed as beasts because they devour sheep-like believers like real beasts ○1 Dn7: Lion, bear+3 ribs stuck (=bitten) between his teeth, leopard+ 4heads, beast+iron teeth [Being bitten = being devoured = one side handed over to other side] [\"Rib\"= woman → pastor (Gn2:21-23); bone = man (Ez37)] ○2 Dn8: Sheep+2 horns; goat+1 horn; 4 horns devour 3 horns →7 horns ○3 Ez38: Meshech, Tubal, Persia, Cush, Put, Beth Togarmah → 7 1 And the dragon stood on the shore of the sea. And I saw a beast coming out of the sea. He had ten horns and seven heads, with ten crowns on his horns, and on each head a blasphemous name. 2 The beast I saw resembled a leopard, but had feet like those of a bear and a mouth like that of a lion. The dragon gave the beast his power and his throne and great authority. 3 One of the heads of the beast seemed to have had a fatal wound, but the fatal wound had been healed. The whole world was astonished and followed the beast. 4 Men worshiped the dragon because he had given authority to the beast, and they also worshiped the beast and asked, \"Who is like the beast? Who can make war against him?\" 5 The beast was given a mouth to utter proud words and blasphemies and to exercise his authority for forty-two months. 6 He opened his mouth to blaspheme God, and to slander his name and his dwelling place and those who live in heaven. 7 He was given power to make war against the saints and to conquer them. And he was given authority over every tribe, people, language and nation. 8 All inhabitants of the earth will worship the beast--all whose names have not been written in the book of life belonging to the Lamb that was slain from the creation of the world. 9 He who has an ear, let him hear. 10 If anyone is to go into captivity, into captivity he will go. If anyone is to be killed with the sword, with the sword he will be killed. This calls for patient endurance and faithfulness on the part of the saints. 11 Then I saw another beast, coming out of the earth. He had two horns like a lamb, but he spoke like a dragon. 12 He exercised all the authority of the first beast on his behalf, and made the earth and its inhabitants worship the first beast, whose fatal wound had been healed. 13 And he performed great and miraculous signs, even causing fire to come down from heaven to earth in full view of men. 14 Because of the signs he was given power to do on behalf of the first beast, he deceived the inhabitants of the earth. He ordered them to set up an image in honor of the beast who was wounded by the sword and yet lived. 15 He was given power to give breath to the image of the first beast, so that it could speak and cause all who refused to worship the image to be killed. 16 He also forced everyone,small and great,rich and poor,free and slave,to receive a mark on his right hand or on his forehead, 17 so that no one could buy or sell unless he had the mark, which is the name of the beast or the number of his name. 18 This calls for wisdom. If anyone has insight, let him calculate the number of the beast, for it is man's number. His number is 666."},{"kind":"notes","page":32,"title":"Notes page 32","text":"\"Dragon gave authority to beast\" Dragon = Satan (Rv12:9) [President gave authority to eliminate cults to S.E.C.] Cf. Jesus gave power & authority to 2 witnesses (Rv11:3) \"One head fatal wound healed\" Pastor Tak hurt in the heart (Zec13:6), because of fight with Kim Jeong-du about becoming head director of SEC, but eventually all problems were well resolved & Tak became head director \"Whole world astonished & followed beast\" Whole tabernacle temple including. 80 branch churches were deceived (Rv17:6) \"Mouth to utter proud words & blasphemies\" Beast was given authority to exalt himself & preach false doctrines on altar \"Exercise authority for 42 months\" 1980.9.14-1984.3.14 \"Conquer them\" Tabernacle temple became Isaac Church \"Book of life\" Registration book of church that is lead by the OWO (Rv20:12, Rv3:12, Rv14:1-3) \"Creation of world\" Creation of the first tabernacle: 1966 March 14 (Rv1:20, Rv2:1) ○1 Adam time: Creation of Garden of Eden ○2 F.C.: Creation of J.B. tabernacle ○3 S.C.: 7golden lampst. \"Those who are killed\" ○1 Rv13: Tabernacle people who betrayed were devoured by beast 7+10 ○2 Rv12: Dragon+ his angles (7+10) were overcome by Michael+ his angels (male child+ his brothers) \"Patient endurance & faithfulness\" Until 42 months are ended, they have to keep their faith and endurance Earthly beast & idols & name of the beast, 666 \"Another beast from earth\" Once was member of tabernacle but later became one with sea beast (gentile) to destroy tabern. \"2 horns like a lamb\" 2 men of authority who came from tabernacle helped Oh to return & take charge again (이희춘 최병준) \"Exercised authority on behalf of first beast\" Sea beast gave power & authority to the earthly beast to rule over tabernacle \"Fire coming from heaven to earth\" Word that kills spirit coming from altar to place where congregation members are \"Beast who was wounded by sword\" Great prostitute = Mr Tak \"Set up image (idol)\" 17 evangelists of tabernacle were anointed as gentile pastors who belong to Satan (destroyers), governing each of the branch churches \"Giving breath to image\" 17 evangelists received word of the beast (doctrine of Satan) and began to teach them to congreg. \"Being killed\" Being kicked out (banished) of the tabernacle \"Receive mark of beast\" Accept doctrine of the beast as truth Cf. Cain's mark (Gn4:15); Adam & Eve's garment of skin (Gn3:21) \"On their right hands\" Taking an oath to Satan by raising their right hands \"On their foreheads\" Anointed as gentile workers by being baptized on their foreheads \"Buy or sell\" Act of receiving or preaching the word in the church \"Small-great, rich-poor\" Pastor & congregation \"Number of the beast = name of the beast = 666\" ○1 At time of Solomon (1Kings10:14, 2Chr9:13) 666 golden talents: Weight of gold Solomon received yearly from gentiles→ gold: word/doctrine Solomon made shields with this gold: Person (Ez39:9: Burning shields = judging gentiles) Large shields (great man like pastor) & small shields (small man like congregation member) ○2 Nebuchadnezzar setting up idol (Dn3) Image is spiritually same as pastor (great man) & its role is that of a shield to protect Nebuchadnezzar from any opposers so that all people will only worship him! Size of image: 6 cubits wide & 60 cubits high"},{"kind":"notes","page":33,"title":"Notes page 33","text":"REVELATION 14: THE HARVESTED & SEALED 144.000 OF THE 12 TRIBES OF MT. ZION \"Names recorded on foreheads\" Being sealed with word of God & Jesus and becoming house of God (Being God's possession) [Cf. Great prostitute on her forehead \"Babylon\": Great prostitute became house of Satan (Rv17:1-5)] \"Harp\" Bible (Rv15:3): Moses' song + song of Lamb (O.T. + N.T.) [Cf.Ps137:1-9: Poplar tree (Samson; Chinese character: Ryu); used to learn song → but now exiled in Babylon → cannot sing song anymore → OWO will judge] \"Harpists\" Those who are victorious over beast & gather in front of sea of glass (Rv15:2) [144.000 are reciting (singing/testifying) words of prophecy in the Bible] \"New song\" Words that have been fulfilled according to word of prophecy = gospel of physical fulfillment [Song: word of prophecy = gospel of prophecy] \"Sung before throne & 4LC & elders\" God and his thrones are coming down upon Mt. Zion dwelling with 144.000 1 Then I looked, and there before me was the Lamb, standing on Mount Zion, and with him 144,000 who had his name and his Father's name written on their foreheads. 2 And I heard a sound from heaven like the roar of rushing waters and like a loud peal of thunder. The sound I heard was like that of harpists playing their harps. 3 And they sang a new song before the throne and before the four living creatures and the elders. No one could learn the song except the 144,000 who had been redeemed from the earth. 4 These are those who did not defile themselves with women, for they kept themselves pure. They follow the Lamb wherever he goes. They were purchased from among men and offered as firstfruits to God and the Lamb. 5 No lie was found in their mouths; they are blameless. 6 Then I saw another angel flying in midair, and he had the eternal gospel to proclaim to those who live on the earth--to every nation, tribe, language and people. 7 He said in a loud voice, \"Fear God and give him glory, because the hour of his judgment has come. Worship him who made the heavens, the earth, the sea and the springs of water.\" 8 A second angel followed and said, \"Fallen! Fallen is Babylon the Great, which made all the nations drink the maddening wine of her adulteries.\" 9 A third angel followed them and said in a loud voice: \"If anyone worships the beast and his image and receives his mark on the forehead or on the hand, 10 he, too, will drink of the wine of God's fury, which has been poured full strength into the cup of his wrath. He will be tormented with burning sulfur in the presence of the holy angels and of the Lamb. 11 And the smoke of their torment rises for ever and ever. There is no rest day or night for those who worship the beast and his image, or for anyone who receives the mark of his name.\" 12 This calls for patient endurance on the part of the saints who obey God's commandments and remain faithful to Jesus. 13 Then I heard a voice from heaven say, \"Write: Blessed are the dead who die in the Lord from now on.\" \"Yes,\" says the Spirit, \"they will rest from their labor, for their deeds will follow them.\" 14 I looked, and there before me was a white cloud, and seated on the cloud was one \"like a son of man\" with a crown of gold on his head and a sharp sickle in his hand. 15 Then another angel came out of the temple and called in a loud voice to him who was sitting on the cloud, \"Take your sickle and reap, because the time to reap has come, for the harvest of the earth is ripe.\" 16 So he who was seated on the cloud swung his sickle over the earth, and the earth was harvested. 17 Another angel came out of the temple in heaven, and he too had a sharp sickle. 18 Still another angel, who had charge of the fire, came from the altar and called in a loud voice to him who had the sharp sickle, \"Take your sharp sickle and gather the clusters of grapes from the earth's vine, because its grapes are ripe.\" 19 The angel swung his sickle on the earth, gathered its grapes and threw them into the great winepress of God's wrath. 20 They w"},{"kind":"notes","page":34,"title":"Notes page 34","text":"\"144.000 redeemed from earth\" With the blood of Jesus = Revelation (Rv1:5-6, Rv5:9-10) → atonement of their sin & purchased from every nation, tribe, language, people → 144.000 are no longer theirs, but Jesus' possession (Gal2:20-21) \"Not defiling themselves with women\" Woman: false pastors including great prostitute (Rv17:5) ○1 Not accepting false doctrine as truth ○2 Maintaining fidelity of their faith \"Firstfruits\" Being born of word of truth (Jam1:18) [cf. 1Cor15:20-24: Jesus= first firstfruit; 144.000; rest] ○1 Prophecy that 2 types of seeds will be scattered (Jer31:27) ○2 Fulfillment: 2 kinds of seeds; good seeds & weed planted in same field (Mt13:24-30,37-39) ○3 Harvest time: Good seeds harvested & going into barn/ Weeds tied in bundle→ burnt (Rv14:14-16) \"No lie found in their mouths; blameless\" 144.000 always testifying word of truth & fulfilling words without adding/subtracting Faith & obedience (cf.Mal2:7-9) 3 angels & result of those who received mark of beast & worshipped image \"Another angel flying in midair\" Counselor Spirit who brought eternal gospel (Rv10:1-2) \"Eternal gospel\" Words that have been fulfilled according to prophecy (word of physical fulfillment) = new song! \"Second angel\" Proclaiming that Babylon has fallen (Rv18:1-2) \"Maddening wine of adulteries\" Commentaries or doctrines made by men's thoughts = Satan's doctrines (Rv17:4, Rv18:3) \"Third angel\" Judgment on those who receive mark of beast & worship image (Rv16:1-2) \"Wine of God's fury\" Word of God's wrath (7 bowls full of God's wrath) → judge both B+D (Rv16,17,18) \"Full strength into cup of his wrath\" Judged by testifying only word of book of revelation without any explanation \"Burning sulfur\" Second death \"Smoke rises for ever\" News that B+D being judged & passed away will be preached forever \"From now on\" After 42months ended & new kingdom of God is established \"Dead who die in Lord\" Those who wash their own dead deeds (sins) with word of life will be able to enter Sabbath-rest Thing that dies in the Lord: Transgressions & sins (Eph2:1) Harvesting of the crops ○1 O.T. prophecy: Jer31:27 ○2 F.C. fulfillment: Mt13:24-30,37-39 ○3 Harvest: Rv14:14-16 \"One like a son of man\" Angel who brings command of Jesus to harvest crops in the field \"Sitting on a cloud\" Angel who is ruling over (governing) many angels (spirits) \"Crown of gold on head\" Receiving position of authority to take charge of harvesting \"Sharp sickle in his hand\" Word of harvesting / One who has word of harvesting \"Another angel coming out of temple\" Angel who proclaims proper time to harvest crops → Harvest begins: ○1 After event of B+D, the event of harvesting would begin from 4 directions - E,W,S,N (Mt24:29-31) ○2 After sun,moon,stars darkened & fallen, Jesus & angels begin harvest from 4 directions (Rv6:12-14) \"Clusters of grapes from earth's vine\" Wild grapes: Tabernacle people who betrayed (Is5:1-7) \"Outside the city\" Outside of the holy city, New Jerusalem: 12 tribes \"Great winepress of God's wrath\" Organization of 7 heads and a beast with 10 horns: S.E.C. = Babylon Betrayers would be thrown into destroyers organization & would be condemned in that place \"Horses bridles\" News/gossip that tabernacle temple was destroyed came out of gentile pastors' mouth \"Distance of 1.600 stadia\" About 300km → News spread all over Korea (since all 80 branch churches were turned over)"},{"kind":"notes","page":35,"title":"Notes page 35","text":"REVELATION 15: THE TEMPLE OF THE TABERNACLE OF TESTIMONY WHERE ALL NATIONS WILL WORSHIP 3 kinds of Plagues in Revelation ○1 Plague of seals (Rv6) → Tabernacle people who betrayed ○2 Plague of trumpets (Rv8,9) → Tabernacle people who betrayed ○3 Plague of bowls (Rv16) → Betrayers and destroyers \"Another great & marvelous sign\" 7 angels with 7 bowls → last plague: Object different from other 2 plagues! \"Heaven\" Second Heaven (New Heaven) \"Sea of glass\" Revealed word that washes inner being of man ○1 Moses time: Bronze basin made from women's mirrors (Ex38:8) ○2 Solomon time: 'Sea' which is used by the priests for washing (2Chr4:6) \"Mixed with fire\" Also contains word of judgment \"Beast, his image, number\" Great prostitute (Rv17), false pastors (Rv13: 17 evangelists), 666 beast (Rv13:11: Earthly beast) \"Those who gather beside sea of glass\" Can sing song of Moses & Lamb because they are witnesses who had seen & heard on spot that the events of revelation would take place (Mt13:52) \"Harp\" Bible (Song of Moses: O.T. prophecy/ Song of Lamb: N.T. prophecy) \"All nation come and worship\" Because God's righteous acts have been revealed \"God's righteous acts\" Acts of salvation: Since work of salvation began & temple of God was opened, all nations would be able to enter God's kingdom to receive salvation \"After this\" After the event of Rv15:2 happened: After those who overcome beast gathered in sea of glass \"Temple of Tabernacle of Testimony\" Temple where events that had happened in tabernacle are testified / Temple where there are witnesses who can testify about what had been seen & heard in tabernacle temple \"7 golden bowls\" People who were victorious over beast & fled to Mt.Zion Qualification is to be able to testify what had been seen & heard in tabernacle \"Dressed in clean linen\" Armed with the word \"Temple filled with smoke\" Word of God's wrath Period of pouring bowls 7 years (Ez39:9): Except B+D, other people can get chance to enter temple within 7 years 1 I saw in heaven another great and marvelous sign: seven angels with the seven last plagues--last, because with them God's wrath is completed. 2 And I saw what looked like a sea of glass mixed with fire and, standing beside the sea, those who had been victorious over the beast and his image and over the number of his name. They held harps given them by God 3 and sang the song of Moses the servant of God and the song of the Lamb: \"Great and marvelous are your deeds, Lord God Almighty. Just and true are your ways, King of the ages. 4 Who will not fear you, O Lord, and bring glory to your name? For you alone are holy. All nations will come and worship before you, for your righteous acts have been revealed.\" 5 After this I looked and in heaven the temple, that is, the tabernacle of the Testimony, was opened. 6 Out of the temple came the seven angels with the seven plagues. They were dressed in clean, shining linen and wore golden sashes around their chests. 7 Then one of the four living creatures gave to the seven angels seven golden bowls filled with the wrath of God, who lives for ever and ever. 8 And the temple was filled with smoke from the glory of God and from his power, and no one could enter the temple until the seven plagues of the seven angels were completed."},{"kind":"notes","page":36,"title":"Notes page 36","text":"REVELATION 12 THE VICTORY OF THE CHILD WHO WILL RULE OVER ALL NATIONS 1-2 A great and wondrous sign in heaven: Woman clothes with sun, moon, 12 stars 3-6 Another sign in heaven & a male child who will rule over all nations 7-13 A war in heaven & dragon being kicked out from heaven 14-17 Woman going back to desert & dragon standing on shore (sand) REVELATION 13 THE CHOSEN PEOPLE WHO BETRAYED & RECEIVED MARK OF THE BEAST 1-10 Beast out of the sea 11-18 Earthly beast & idols & name of beast, 666 REVELATION 14 THE HARVESTED & SEALED 144.000 OF THE 12 TRIBES OF MT. ZION 1-5 144.000 people on Mt. Zion 6-13 3 angels & result of those who received mark of the beast & worshipped the image 14-20 Harvest & judgment outside the city REVELATION 15 THE TEMPLE OF THE TABERNACLE OF THE TESTIMONY WHERE ALL NATIONS WILL WORSHIP 1-4 The last plagues & those who had been victorious over the beast, his image, and number of his name 5-8 The Temple of the Tabernacle of Testimony & the 7 plagues of the 7 angels REVELATION 16 THE 7 BOWLS OF GOD'S WRATH 1-2 1st bowl: Land (ugly & painful sores) 3 2nd bowl: Sea (turned into blood & every livin 4-7 3rd bowl: Rivers & springs of water (became blood & blood to drink as they deserve) 8-9 4th bowl: Sun (given power to scorch people with fire & intense heat) 10-11 5th bowls: Throne of beast (kingdom plunged into darkness & men gnawed tongues in agony) 12-16 6th bowl: Great river Euphrates (water dried up to prepare way for kings from East) 17-21 7th bowl: Air (tremendous earthquake & wind of the fury of God's wrath & huge hailstones) REVELATION 17 WINE OF ADULTERIES, AND THE MYSTERY OF THE PROSTITUTE AND THE BEAST 1-5 The great prostitute sitting on the many waters which are the dragon with 7 heads & 10 horns 6-14 The mystery of the 7 heads & 10 horns 15-18 The punishment of the great prostitute REVELATION 18 BABYLON, HOME OF DEMONS AND ALL FALLEN NATIONS 1-3 Another angel coming down from heaven & the maddening wine 4-8 The fall of the great prostitute & the punishment on her 9-13 The kings of the earth & the merchants that will mourn & cry & the cargoes of Babylon 14-19 The fruit Babylon longed for & the sea captain, the sailors, all who travel by ship 20-24 The vengeance of blood on Babylon"},{"kind":"notes","page":37,"title":"Notes page 37","text":"REVELATION 16: THE TEMPLE OF THE TABERNACLE OF TESTIMONY WHERE ALL NATIONS WILL WORSHIP FIRST BOWL → \"Land\" Tabernacle temple \"Ugly & painful sores\" Transgression & sins or faults (=shamefulness) → Betrayers were tortured because their sins & shamefulness had been exposed publicly SECOND BOWL →\"Sea\" World that had been ruled by the prostitute (Babylon) \"Sea\" Many waters = gentile doctrines \"Blood like of dead man\" Their doctrines were revealed as untruth (false doctrines) \"Every living things\" Every denomination of the congregation members in the worldly churches \"Die\" They cannot testify the gentile doctrines that they have believed as truth 1 Then I heard a loud voice from the temple saying to the seven angels, \"Go, pour out the seven bowls of God's wrath on the earth.\" 2 The first angel went and poured out his bowl on the land, and ugly and painful sores broke out on the people who had the mark of the beast and worshiped his image. 3 The second angel poured out his bowl on the sea, and it turned into blood like that of a dead man, and every living thing in the sea died. 4 The third angel poured out his bowl on the rivers and springs of water, and they became blood. 5 Then I heard the angel in charge of the waters say: \"You are just in these judgments, you who are and who were, the Holy One, because you have so judged; 6 for they have shed the blood of your saints and prophets, and you have given them blood to drink as they deserve.\" 7 And I heard the altar respond: \"Yes, Lord God Almighty, true and just are your judgments.\" 8 The fourth angel poured out his bowl on the sun, and the sun was given power to scorch people with fire. 9 They were seared by the intense heat and they cursed the name of God, who had control over these plagues, but they refused to repent and glorify him. 10 The fifth angel poured out his bowl on the throne of the beast, and his kingdom was plunged into darkness. Men gnawed their tongues in agony 11 and cursed the God of heaven because of their pains and their sores, but they refused to repent of what they had done. 12 The sixth angel poured out his bowl on the great river Euphrates, and its water was dried up to prepare the way for the kings from the East. 13 Then I saw three evil spirits that looked like frogs; they came out of the mouth of the dragon, out of the mouth of the beast and out of the mouth of the false prophet. 14 They are spirits of demons performing miraculous signs, and they go out to the kings of the whole world, to gather them for the battle on the great day of God Almighty. 15 \"Behold, I come like a thief! Blessed is he who stays awake and keeps his clothes with him, so that he may not go naked and be shamefully exposed.\" 16 Then they gathered the kings together to the place that in Hebrew is called Armageddon. 17 The seventh angel poured out his bowl into the air, and out of the temple came a loud voice from the throne, saying, \"It is done!\" 18 Then there came flashes of lightning, rumblings, peals of thunder and a severe earthquake. No earthquake like it has ever occurred since man has been on earth, so tremendous was the quake. 19 The great city split into three parts, and the cities of the nations collapsed. God remembered Babylon the Great and gave her the cup filled with the wine of the fury of his wrath. 20 Every island fled away and the mountains could not be found. 21 From the sky huge hailstones of about a hundred pounds each fell upon men. And they cursed God on account of the plague of hail, because the plague was so terrible."},{"kind":"notes","page":38,"title":"Notes page 38","text":"THIRD BOWL → \"Rivers & springs of water\" False evangelists & pastors who killed spirits of men with bitter water which was given to them by the fallen star in Rv8:10-11 \"Becoming blood\" Their doctrines became dead doctrines \"Blood to drink as they deserve\" God would make the rivers & springs of water eat the bitter food and drink poisoned water because they had done such a thing to chosen people of God before (Jer23:15, Rv8:10-11) \"Judgment is true & just\" As written in the books according to what they have done (Rv20:12) FOURTH BOWL → \"Sun\" False pastor (cf.Mt13:6) \"Fire\" Word of judgment, but here, word that the false pastor pour out on his own congregation with anger \"Scorch people\" Spirits of people would be killed by the false pastor's word like fire \"Intense heat\" False doctrines that can harm or kill the spirits of people (cf. 1Pt1:24: grass/flower=people) FIFTH BOWL → \"Throne of Beast\" Tabernacle temple: since it was handed over to gentile it became throne/nation of beast \"Kingdom was plunged into darkness\" They could not testify their doctrines as truth \"Men gnawed their tongues in agony\" Because their shamefulness & transgressions had been revealed publicly SIXTH BOWL → \"Great river Euphrates\" Headquarter of destroyers: Place from where group of Satan came out (Rv9:14) \"Water was dried up\" Gentile doctrines were judged & disappeared \"Kings from the East\" 144.000 (first fruits) from first tabernacle temple because God's work began from that place \"Dragon\" Head pastor who is ruling over Babylon (7+10 beast) \"Beast\" 666 number beast = earthly beast \"False prophet\" Idol or image which was set up by the earthly beast \"Kings of whole world\" Pastors in the world who belong to dragon \"Armageddon\" Battle field between chosen people & gentile Spiritual battlefield at revelation time: Tabernacle Temple (Rv12, Rv13) Today's battlefield: Babylon \"Clothes\" Righteous acts: Keep the word / Naked: ○1 Forsaken God's word [○2 Being dead (2Cor5)] SEVENTH BOWL → \"Air\" Rumor/press/broadcasting \"Quake were tremendous because no earthquake has ever occurred on earth\" Tabernacle would be divided into 3 parts ○1 Organization of betrayers: Tabernacle temple (now 소망교회) ○2 Organization of destroyers: Babylon ○3 Organization of savior: SCJ (NHNE) \"Wind of fury of God's wrath\" Word of God's wrath \"Every island & mountain\" Branch churches which belonged to the gentile \"Fled away\" All denomination or church names have been changed \"Huge hailstones about hundred pound\" Promised pastor who received the word of God's wrath from God had such weight"},{"kind":"notes","page":39,"title":"Notes page 39","text":"REVELATION 17: WINE OF ADULTERIES AND THE MYSTERY OF THE PROSTITUTE AND THE BEAST MYSTERY OF GREAT PROSTITUTE \"Great prostitute\" Head of Babylon ruling over the whole world with organization of 7 heads & 10 horns: S.E.C. (Rv17:3) \"Many waters\" People, multitudes, nations, languages (Rv17:15) \"Kings of the earth\" Pastors who belong to the great prostitute \"Inhabitants of earth\" Congregation members who belong to the false pastors in the world (=kings of the earth) \"Committing adultery\" Receiving the seed of Satan & associating with Satan's pastor \"Maddening wine\" Commentaries or Satan's doctrines \"Desert\" Place without God's word (=water); Place where wild beasts dwell; Place of Satan's deception (cf.Mt4) \"Blasphemous names\" Positions of authority made by men (not given by God) to destroy God's temple \"Purple & scarlet\" False doctrines or teachings of the dragon (=Satan) \"Gold, precious stones\" Every kind of gentile doctrines \"Golden cup\" Bible [Gold: Word of truth (Mt13:44-46)], but here, commentary Bible 1 One of the seven angels who had the seven bowls came and said to me, \"Come, I will show you the punishment of the great prostitute, who sits on many waters. 2 With her the kings of the earth committed adultery and the inhabitants of the earth were intoxicated with the wine of her adulteries.\" 3 Then the angel carried me away in the Spirit into a desert. There I saw a woman sitting on a scarlet beast that was covered with blasphemous names and had seven heads and ten horns. 4 The woman was dressed in purple and scarlet, and was glittering with gold, precious stones and pearls. She held a golden cup in her hand, filled with abominable things and the filth of her adulteries. 5 This title was written on her forehead: MYSTERY BABYLON THE GREAT THE MOTHER OF PROSTITUTES AND OF THE ABOMINATIONS OF THE EARTH. 6 I saw that the woman was drunk with the blood of the saints, the blood of those who bore testimony to Jesus. When I saw her, I was greatly astonished. 7 Then the angel said to me: \"Why are you astonished? I will explain to you the mystery of the woman and of the beast she rides, which has the seven heads and ten horns. 8 The beast, which you saw, once was, now is not, and will come up out of the Abyss and go to his destruction. The inhabitants of the earth whose names have not been written in the book of life from the creation of the world will be astonished when they see the beast, because he once was, now is not, and yet will come. 9 \"This calls for a mind with wisdom. The seven heads are seven hills on which the woman sits. 10 They are also seven kings. Five have fallen, one is, the other has not yet come; but when he does come, he must remain for a little while. 11 The beast who once was, and now is not, is an eighth king. He belongs to the seven and is going to his destruction. 12 \"The ten horns you saw are ten kings who have not yet received a kingdom, but who for one hour will receive authority as kings along with the beast. 13 They have one purpose and will give their power and authority to the beast. 14 They will make war against the Lamb, but the Lamb will overcome them because he is Lord of lords and King of kings--and with him will be his called, chosen and faithful followers.\" 15 Then the angel said to me, \"The waters you saw, where the prostitute sits, are peoples, multitudes, nations and languages. 16 The beast and the ten horns you saw will hate the prostitute. They will bring her to ruin and leave her naked; they will eat her flesh and burn her with fire. 17 For God has put it into their hearts to accomplish his purpose by agreeing to give the beast their power to rule, until God's words are fulfilled. 18 The woman you saw is the great city that rules over the kings of the earth.\""},{"kind":"notes","page":40,"title":"Notes page 40","text":"\"Abominable things & filth of her adulteries\" Commentaries & doctrines made by men's thoughts (Gal1:11-12, Mt15, Jn8:44) \"Name on her forehead: Babylon the Great\" Great prostitute would be a home for demons, a haunt for every evil spirit (Rv18:2) \"Mother of Prostitutes & of abominations of the earth\" Great prostitute received the seed of Satan from the evil spirit & gave birth to many prostitutes as mother (=queen, Rv18:7) → Higher position than any other pastor MYSTERY OF THE 7 HEADS & 10 HORNS \"Being drunk with\" Accepting/acknowledging (cf.Dn4:34-37) \"Blood of saints & witnesses\" Word of testimony which the saints and witnesses would deliver → Heart of prostitute was greatly shaken after hearing word of testimony, but refused to repent of her adulteries (Rv2:21) → She would be thrown into bed of suffering which is the second death (Rv20:15, Rv21:8, Rv19:20) \"Being astonished\" Being deceived: If mystery wasn't made known→ anyone could be deceived & follow woman (Rv13:3) \"Beast who once was, who is not, but who will come up out of the Abyss & go to destruction\" First Mr Oh became headpastor of tabernacle, bit later when tabernacle was changed into Isaac church he began to reign over the tabernacle. After Mr Ryu left for the US, Mr Oh was forced to get down from his position for a while & went to Jejudo and then to Uijeongbu. In May 1981 he was appointed as general secretary in S.E.C, and finally was able to return & take charge of tabernacle with the help of 2 horns. In April 1984, after 42 months ended, he was kicked out from tabernacle (Rv17:11: \"go to destruction\") and went to the US. \"Creation of the world\" When tabernacle (church of 7 golden lampstands) was established (Rv1:20, Rv2:1) \"Book of life\" Registration book of the church led by the OWO (Rv20:12, Rv3:12, Rv14) \"Inhabitants of earth\" Tabernacle people who betrayed (Rv13) \"7 heads\" 7 hills = 7 mountains = 7 denominations (churches): They possess their own denominations (churches) \"7 kings\" 7 pastors (1Pt2:9): They are all gentile pastors controlled by evil spirits \"5 have fallen, one is, the other has not yet come\" Order by which they have been concerned with the tabernacle: 5 out of 7 heads have already left tabernacle, prostitute still remains, and Tak Myeong-hwan (older brother of prostitute) would come up to tabernacle after he made his own church (국종교회). \"8th king\" Because he overtook tabernacle & Babylon from prostitute after he drove out 7 heads \"Belongs to 7\" He was not one of 7 heads but he belonged to the 7 & worked with them to destroy the tabernacle \"10 horns\" 10 elders of tabernacle appointed by Presbyterian law Originally there were 12 elders in tabernacle temple, but in 1980 September 14 when tabernacle was handed over to gentile, only 10 would be appointed as new 10 elders. \"10 kings\" They acted like a pastor for some time while Mr Oh was absent, and gave sermon on altar by turns \"Not received kingdom\" They had no church of their own \"One purpose\" To bring prostitute to ruin [cf.Dn2: Iron+clay = gentile+tabernacle: United at first, but later broken up] \"Lord of lords & King of kings\" Jesus & 144.000 \"His called, chosen, faithful followers\" Spiritual Passover (Rv18:4) ○1 Moses time (Ex12): Egypt→Canaan ○2 F.C.:Pharisees, teachers of law→Jesus ○3 S.C.: Babylon→Mt. Zion (NHNE) [Event connected to Rv12.17] PUNISHMENT OF THE GREAT PROSTITUTE \"Eating her flesh\" Using & accepting doctrines of great prostitute as their own languages (doctrines) [cf. flesh & blood of Jesus= word of Jesus (Jn6:51-58)] \"Burning her with fire\" As they disclosed the prostitutes wicked things publicly, she could not keep her position anymore →Beast & 10 horns would kick her out from Babylon (S.E.C.) [cf. woman Jezebel (2Kg9:10)] \"Until God's words fulfilled\" Until 42 months (period of destruction) ended \"Great city\" As Jesus is the great city of God (Jn2:19-21), the great prostitute is city of Satan (=a home for demons or a haunt for every evil spirit) → Just like God, Jesus, and"},{"kind":"notes","page":41,"title":"Notes page 41","text":"REVELATION 18: BABYLON, HOME OF DEMONS & ALL FALLEN NATIONS ANOTHER ANGEL COMING DOWN FROM HEAVEN & MADDENING WINE \"After this\" After the great prostitute was judged in Rv17 \"Another angel\" Angel different from angel who had shown judgment of prostitute \"Earth illuminated by splendor\" Those who don't perceive & understand God's word (ignorant people of the world) were awakened & being enlightened by the word of God like light \"Babylon the Great\" Great prostitute (Rv17:5) → House of Satan \"Maddening wine of adulteries\" Commentaries or Satan's doctrines ○1Fruit of knowledge of good & evil (Gn2:17, Col2:21-22) ○2 Traditions of elders (Mt15), other gospel (Gal1:8-9) \"Merchants of the earth\" Evangelists who belong to the great prostitute 1 After this I saw another angel coming down from heaven. He had great authority, and the earth was illuminated by his splendor. 2 With a mighty voice he shouted: \"Fallen! Fallen is Babylon the Great! She has become a home for demons and a haunt for every evil spirit, a haunt for every unclean and detestable bird. 3 For all the nations have drunk the maddening wine of her adulteries. The kings of the earth committed adultery with her, and the merchants of the earth grew rich from her excessive luxuries.\" 4 Then I heard another voice from heaven say: \"Come out of her, my people, so that you will not share in her sins, so that you will not receive any of her plagues; 5 for her sins are piled up to heaven, and God has remembered her crimes. 6 Give back to her as she has given; pay her back double for what she has done. Mix her a double portion from her own cup. 7 Give her as much torture and grief as the glory and luxury she gave herself. In her heart she boasts, 'I sit as queen; I am not a widow, and I will never mourn.' 8 Therefore in one day her plagues will overtake her: death, mourning and famine. She will be consumed by fire, for mighty is the Lord God who judges her. 9 \"When the kings of the earth who committed adultery with her and shared her luxury see the smoke of her burning, they will weep and mourn over her. 10 Terrified at her torment, they will stand far off and cry: \"'Woe! Woe, O great city, O Babylon, city of power! In one hour your doom has come!' 11 \"The merchants of the earth will weep and mourn over her because no one buys their cargoes any more-- 12 cargoes of gold, silver, precious stones and pearls; fine linen, purple, silk and scarlet cloth; every sort of citron wood, and articles of every kind made of ivory, costly wood, bronze, iron and marble; 13 cargoes of cinnamon and spice, of incense, myrrh and frankincense, of wine and olive oil, of fine flour and wheat; cattle and sheep; horses and carriages; and bodies and souls of men. 14 \"They will say, 'The fruit you longed for is gone from you. All your riches and splendor have vanished, never to be recovered.' 15 The merchants who sold these things and gained their wealth from her will stand far off, terrified at her torment. They will weep and mourn 16 and cry out: \"'Woe! Woe, O great city, dressed in fine linen, purple and scarlet, and glittering with gold, precious stones and pearls! 17 In one hour such great wealth has been brought to ruin!' \"Every sea captain, and all who travel by ship, the sailors, and all who earn their living from the sea, will stand far off. 18 When they see the smoke of her burning, they will exclaim, 'Was there ever a city like this great city?' 19 They will throw dust on their heads, and with weeping and mourning cry out: \"'Woe! Woe, O great city, where all who had ships on the sea became rich through her wealth! In one hour she has been brought to ruin! 20 Rejoice over her, O heaven! Rejoice, saints and apostles and prophets! God has judged her for the way she treated you.'\" 21 Then a mighty angel picked up a boulder the size of a large millstone and threw it into the sea, and said: \"With such violence the great city of Babylon will be thrown down, never to be found again. 22 The music of harpists "},{"kind":"notes","page":42,"title":"Notes page 42","text":"\"Excessive luxuries\" Babylonian cargoes: The evangelists received power & authority from great prostitute, selling cargoes of Babylon & growing rich (Rv18:12-13) FALL OF THE GREAT PROSTITUTE & PUNISHMENT ON HER \"Another voice from heaven\" Jesus' voice (Rv17:14) \"Pay her back double\" Since great prostitute had overcome tabernacle for 42m, she would receive punishment for 7y [7 bowls of Rv16: punishment of Babylon. Ez39:9: For all weapons of gentile burnt out for 7y] \"Sitting as queen\" She was in higher position than any other pastor [Angel of the Abyss as king (Rv9:11)] \"Not a widow\" Insisted that she is pastor (bride) with whom Jesus (bridegroom) is, but actually bride of Satan! \"Consumed by fire\" Being condemned to disappear by word of judgment KINGS OF THE EARTH & MERCHANTS THAT WILL MOURN & CRY \"Smoke of her burning\" News that great prostitute has been ruined (fallen) \"Merchants mourn & cry\" Because no one buys their cargoes CARGOES OF BABYLON \"Gold, silver, precious stones & pearls\" Various kinds of gentile doctrines \"Fine linen, purple, silk, scarlet cloth\" Babylonian teaching laws \"Citron wood, ivory, costly wood, bronze, iron, marble\" Various kinds of organizations or gatherings (e.g. IBF, CCC, YMCA etc) \"Cinnamon & spice, incense, myrrh, frankincense\" Babylonian laws concerning offerings & prayers \"Wine, olive oil, fine flour, wheat\" False testimony of Babylon \"Cattle, sheep, horses, carriages, bodies, souls of men\" Physical & spiritual workers who belong to Satan FRUIT BABYLON LONGED FOR & SEA CAPTAIN, SAILORS, ALL WHO TRAVEL BY SHIP \"Fruit you longed for\" People of God who have been in exiles in Babylon (Rv17:14, Rv18:4) \"Sea captain, sailors, all who travel by ship\" Church, pastor, evangelists or church workers, congregation members VENGEANCE OF BLOOD ON BABYLON \"God judged her for way she treated you\" Vengeance of blood of beheaded (cf. 5th seal) → fulfilled in Rv18:20 \"Boulder size of large millstone\" Great prostitute & his organization (Babylon, SE.C.) \"Being thrown down into sea, never to be found again\" Babylon would be deserted into the world; no more such organization \"Music of harpists & musicians\" Commentary Bibles made by gentile pastors \"Music of flute players & trumpeters\" False testimony made by false pastors \"Workman of any trade\" Workers that buy & sell false doctrines \"Sound of a millstone\" Sound made by research worker who makes many commentaries \"Light of a lamp\" False doctrine of false pastor \"Bridegroom & bride\" Evil spirits & pastors or congregation members who belong to Satan \"Magic spell\" False omen or false revelation \"Blood of the prophets & saints & all who have been killed on earth found in Babylon\" Babylon has finally been revealed as culprit that has killed all the prophets & saints of God until now"},{"kind":"notes","page":43,"title":"Notes page 43","text":"REVELATION 19: THE WEDDING BANQUET OF THE LAMB VICTORY OF GOD & THE BRIDE OF THE LAMB \"After this\" After Babylon was fallen & judged \"Great multitude in heaven\" 144.000 on Mt. Zion (Rv14:1-2) → sound like roar of rushing waters & loud peals of thunder (Rv19:6) \"Judgment true & just\" Done as written in books according to what they have done 1 After this I heard what sounded like the roar of a great multitude in heaven shouting: \"Hallelujah! Salvation and glory and power belong to our God, 2 for true and just are his judgments. He has condemned the great prostitute who corrupted the earth by her adulteries. He has avenged on her the blood of his servants.\" 3 And again they shouted: \"Hallelujah! The smoke from her goes up for ever and ever.\" 4 The twenty-four elders and the four living creatures fell down and worshiped God, who was seated on the throne. And they cried: \"Amen, Hallelujah!\" 5 Then a voice came from the throne, saying:\"Praise our God, all you his servants, you who fear him, both small and great!\" 6 Then I heard what sounded like a great multitude, like the roar of rushing waters and like loud peals of thunder, shouting: \"Hallelujah! For our Lord God Almighty reigns. 7 Let us rejoice and be glad and give him glory! For the wedding of the Lamb has come, and his bride has made herself ready. 8 Fine linen, bright and clean, was given her to wear.\" (Fine linen stands for the righteous acts of the saints.) 9 Then the angel said to me, \"Write: 'Blessed are those who are invited to the wedding supper of the Lamb!'\" And he added, \"These are the true words of God.\" 10 At this I fell at his feet to worship him. But he said to me, \"Do not do it! I am a fellow servant with you and with your brothers who hold to the testimony of Jesus. Worship God! For the testimony of Jesus is the spirit of prophecy.\" 11 I saw heaven standing open and there before me was a white horse, whose rider is called Faithful and True. With justice he judges and makes war. 12 His eyes are like blazing fire, and on his head are many crowns. He has a name written on him that no one knows but he himself. 13 He is dressed in a robe dipped in blood, and his name is the Word of God. 14 The armies of heaven were following him, riding on white horses and dressed in fine linen, white and clean. 15 Out of his mouth comes a sharp sword with which to strike down the nations. \"He will rule them with an iron scepter.\" He treads the winepress of the fury of the wrath of God Almighty. 16 On his robe and on his thigh he has this name written: KING OF KINGS AND LORD OF LORDS. 17 And I saw an angel standing in the sun, who cried in a loud voice to all the birds flying in midair, \"Come, gather together for the great supper of God, 18 so that you may eat the flesh of kings, generals, and mighty men, of horses and their riders, and the flesh of all people, free and slave, small and great.\" 19 Then I saw the beast and the kings of the earth and their armies gathered together to make war against the rider on the horse and his army. 20 But the beast was captured, and with him the false prophet who had performed the miraculous signs on his behalf. With these signs he had deluded those who had received the mark of the beast and worshiped his image. The two of them were thrown alive into the fiery lake of burning sulfur. 21 The rest of them were killed with the sword that came out of the mouth of the rider on the horse, and all the birds gorged themselves on their flesh."},{"kind":"notes","page":44,"title":"Notes page 44","text":"\"Avenging on her blood of his servants\" Vengeance of the blood done in Rv18:20-24 \"Smoke from her goes up for ever and ever\" News of punishment of great prostitute & her kingdom spread over whole world Evidence of wedding banquet God's oxen & fattened cattle: B+D (Mt22:King: God, son: Jesus + his bride) \"Flesh of kings, generals, mighty men, of horses & their riders, and of all people, free & slave, small & great\" (Rv19:18) Participants of wedding banquet Spirits of the martyrs & the saints of God \"Bride of Lamb allowed to wear fine linen\" Bride will receive glory from many people through the righteous acts of her saints \"Testimony of Jesus\" \"Spirit of prophecy\" → speak on behalf ○1 Counselor spirit: Angel who speaks on behalf of Jesus in spiritual realm ○2 Pastor like John (flesh):Counselor who speaks on behalf in physic. realm (Rv10:11) THE VICTORY OF A WHITE HORSE & ITS RIDER \"White horse & its rider\" Promised pastor & Jesus (Is31:3: flesh, Rv6:1-2: 1st seal, Rv3:14: faithful & true) \"Many crowns\" Much authority \"Name no one knows but he himself\" Jesus received God's new name (word) & came in name of God (Jn5:43) → Jesus new name: OWO (Rv2:17, Rv3:12) \"Dressed in a robe dipped in blood\" Being armed with God's word (Rv19:13, Jn6:63) → war against enemy (Ep6:12-17) \"Sharp sword\" Word of judgment (Heb4:12-14, Ep6:17) \"Winepress\" Organization of destroyers = 7 heads & beast with 10 horns \"Fury of wrath of God Almighty\" Word of the Bible filled with God's wrath \"Angel standing in the sun\" Angel who works with the promised pastor of God (sun) \"All birds flying in midair\" Spirits of the martyrs that would be invited to wedding supper of the Lamb \"Beast & kings of earth & armies\" Prostitute & pastors of the world & congregation members \"Gathered to make war\" Armageddon (Rv12, Rv16 → Rv19:19) \"Beast & false prophet\" Great prostitute & wormwood \"Being thrown alive into fiery lake of burning sulfur\" Even though they are physically alive, their judgment would be destined to go to 2nd death→ No chance for sins to be forgiven or to be saved (F.C.:Phar+Sad) \"The rest of them\" Branch churches of S.E.C. \"All birds gorged themselves on their flesh\" All martyr spirits satisfied with words that B+D have been condemned & judged -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- *Time periods in book of Daniel in time of Revelation ○1 2300 days (Dn8): 1984 March 14 (Temple of tabernacle of Testimony)→ 1990 (first mission center) ○2 1290 days (Dn12:11): 1980 September 14 (Isaac Church)→ 1984 March 14 (42 months end)→ 1984 April (Mr Oh kicked out) ○3 1335 days (Dn12:12): 1980 September 14→ 1984 June (first time physical temple in Bisan-dong)"},{"kind":"notes","page":45,"title":"Notes page 45","text":"REVELATION 20: THE MILLENNIAL CITY, THE FIRST RESURRECTION THE FIRST RESURRECTION \"Key of the Abyss\" Wisdom & authority to make angels of Satan come into or out of Abyss \"Great chain\" Word of testimony with which to catch the dragon (Satan) Wormwood had key in order to punish betrayers (Rv9). After 42 months, dragon hurled down to earth because he was defeated by God's armies (Rv12:7-9). The authority (key) that had been given to him for a while would be handed over to the angel of God who would seize & lock the dragon \"Locked up for 1.000 years\" ○1 To heal all nations that have been deceived by Satan for 6.000 years ○2 Not to deceive the whole world (with Satan's interruption world won't be healed again) \"Set free for a short while\" To separate those who believe & those who don't: After the 1.000 years those who don't believe in God (word) would go into second death after being deceived by the dragon & attacking city of God → punished in the burning lake of sulfur forever 1 And I saw an angel coming down out of heaven, having the key to the Abyss and holding in his hand a great chain. 2 He seized the dragon, that ancient serpent, who is the devil, or Satan, and bound him for a thousand years. 3 He threw him into the Abyss, and locked and sealed it over him, to keep him from deceiving the nations anymore until the thousand years were ended. After that, he must be set free for a short time. 4 I saw thrones on which were seated those who had been given authority to judge. And I saw the souls of those who had been beheaded because of their testimony for Jesus and because of the word of God. They had not worshiped the beast or his image and had not received his mark on their foreheads or their hands. They came to life and reigned with Christ a thousand years. 5 (The rest of the dead did not come to life until the thousand years were ended.) This is the first resurrection. 6 Blessed and holy are those who have part in the first resurrection. The second death has no power over them, but they will be priests of God and of Christ and will reign with him for a thousand years. 7 When the thousand years are over, Satan will be released from his prison 8 and will go out to deceive the nations in the four corners of the earth--Gog and Magog--to gather them for battle. In number they are like the sand on the seashore. 9 They marched across the breadth of the earth and surrounded the camp of God's people, the city he loves. But fire came down from heaven and devoured them. 10 And the devil, who deceived them, was thrown into the lake of burning sulfur, where the beast and the false prophet had been thrown. They will be tormented day and night for ever and ever. 11 Then I saw a great white throne and him who was seated on it. Earth and sky fled from his presence, and there was no place for them. 12 And I saw the dead, great and small, standing before the throne, and books were opened. Another book was opened, which is the book of life. The dead were judged according to what they had done as recorded in the books. 13 The sea gave up the dead that were in it, and death and Hades gave up the dead that were in them, and each person was judged according to what he had done. 14 Then death and Hades were thrown into the lake of fire. The lake of fire is the second death. 15 If anyone's name was not found written in the book of life, he was thrown into the lake of fire."},{"kind":"notes","page":46,"title":"Notes page 46","text":"\"Authority to judge\" Priests of God = 12 tribes 144.000 \"First resurrection\" Holy City New Jerusalem descend upon 12 tribes & God's dwelling place will be with them (Rv21:1-4) (1Cor15:51-54, 2Cor5:1-5) Participants: ○1 The souls of those who had been beheaded (martyr spirits) ○2 Those who hadn't worshiped beast,image, nor received mark on foreheads/ hands \"Rest of the dead\" All who are dead in Christ, but not taking part in first resurrection: Cannot come to life again with flesh, but after 1.000 years, they will be resurrected & go to heaven SATAN'S DOOM AFTER 1.000 YEARS \"Gog & Magog\" Organization of Satan like Babylon (cf.Ez38) \"4 corners of the earth\" 4 directions that the city of God (Holy City New Jerusalem) is centered on \"Like sand on seashore\" Their armies will be so huge that they cannot be counted \"Camp of God's people\" 12 tribes of 144.000 & GMW \"Fire coming from heaven\" Physical fire will consume (kill) the enemy (=like time of Lot) \"Beast & false prophet\" Great prostitute & wormwood JUDGMENT AFTER 1.000 YEARS \"Great white throne\" Throne of God \"Earth\" Saints who belong to sky (=mission centers) \"Sky\" Mission centers which belong to 12 tribes: Mission centers last for 1.000 years in order to heal all nations, but will then be closed because the last judgment would be made in whole world. People who are then still studying the Bible in the mission center will be saved & go to heaven without judgment or punishment \"Books were opened\" Scriptures: 66 books (Bible) \"Book of life\" Registration book of the church led by OWO: Whether alive or physically dead, all people will come in front of God's throne & will be judged as written in the books according to what they have done \"Sea\" World \"Death & Hades\" Satan's dwelling place = organization of Satan \"Gave up the dead\" Spiritual dead, but physically alive: Not be able to possess any person as their own inheritance \"Second death\" Eternal punishment: Spirit will be tormented in the burning lake of sulfur for ever & ever REVELATION 19 THE WEDDING BANQUET OF THE LAMB 1-10 The victory of God & the bride of the Lamb 11-21 The victory of a white horse & its rider REVELATION 20 THE MILLENNIAL CITY, THE FIRST RESURRECTION 1-6 The first resurrection 7-11 Satan's doom after 1.000 years 12-15 The judgment after 1.000 years"},{"kind":"notes","page":47,"title":"Notes page 47","text":"REVELATION 21: THE NEW HEAVEN & NEW EARTH, AND THE HOLY CITY NEW HEAVEN & NEW EARTH, FIRST HEAVEN & FIRST EARTH, SEA \"New heaven & new earth\" New Tabernacle = second tabernacle & new saints (2Pt3:13, Rv7, Rv14:1-5, Rv15:2-5) Creation of NHNE ○1 Born of seed of God (Lk8:11, Jn3:3-5) ○2 Being harvested (Mt13:24-30, Rv14:14-16) ○3 Being sealed (Rv7:1-8) \"First heaven\" First tabernacle who betrayed = tabernacle temple \"First earth\" People (congregation) who belong to tabernacle (who received mark of beast in Rv13) \"Passed away\" FHFE passed away because they had been destroyed by Satan's organization called Babylon 1 Then I saw a new heaven and a new earth, for the first heaven and the first earth had passed away, and there was no longer any sea. 2 I saw the Holy City, the new Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God, prepared as a bride beautifully dressed for her husband. 3 And I heard a loud voice from the throne saying, \"Now the dwelling of God is with men, and he will live with them. They will be his people, and God himself will be with them and be their God. 4 He will wipe every tear from their eyes. There will be no more death or mourning or crying or pain, for the old order of things has passed away.\" 5 He who was seated on the throne said, \"I am making everything new!\" Then he said, \"Write this down, for these words are trustworthy and true.\" 6 He said to me: \"It is done. I am the Alpha and the Omega, the Beginning and the End. To him who is thirsty I will give to drink without cost from the spring of the water of life. 7 He who overcomes will inherit all this, and I will be his God and he will be my son. 8 But the cowardly, the unbelieving, the vile, the murderers, the sexually immoral, those who practice magic arts, the idolaters and all liars--their place will be in the fiery lake of burning sulfur. This is the second death.\" 9 One of the seven angels who had the seven bowls full of the seven last plagues came and said to me, \"Come, I will show you the bride, the wife of the Lamb.\" 10 And he carried me away in the Spirit to a mountain great and high, and showed me the Holy City, Jerusalem, coming down out of heaven from God. 11 It shone with the glory of God, and its brilliance was like that of a very precious jewel, like a jasper, clear as crystal. 12 It had a great, high wall with twelve gates, and with twelve angels at the gates. On the gates were written the names of the twelve tribes of Israel. 13 There were three gates on the east, three on the north, three on the south and three on the west. 14 The wall of the city had twelve foundations, and on them were the names of the twelve apostles of the Lamb. 15 The angel who talked with me had a measuring rod of gold to measure the city, its gates and its walls. 16 The city was laid out like a square, as long as it was wide. He measured the city with the rod and found it to be 12,000 stadia in length, and as wide and high as it is long. 17 He measured its wall and it was 144 cubits thick, by man's measurement, which the angel was using. 18 The wall was made of jasper, and the city of pure gold, as pure as glass. 19 The foundations of the city walls were decorated with every kind of precious stone. The first foundation was jasper, the second sapphire, the third chalcedony, the fourth emerald, 20 the fifth sardonyx, the sixth carnelian, the seventh chrysolite, the eighth beryl, the ninth topaz, the tenth chrysoprase, the eleventh jacinth, and the twelfth amethyst. 21 The twelve gates were twelve pearls, each gate made of a single pearl. The great street of the city was of pure gold, like transparent glass. 22 I did not see a temple in the city, because the Lord God Almighty and the Lamb are its temple. 23 The city does not need the sun or the moon to shine on it, for the glory of God gives it light, and the Lamb is its lamp. 24 The nations will walk by its light, and the kings of the earth will bring their splendor into it. 25 On no day will its gates ever be shut, fo"},{"kind":"notes","page":48,"title":"Notes page 48","text":"\"Sea\" World = Satan's organization (the beast) = 7+10 beasts (Rv17:3,15) \"No more sea\" Dragon & his angels defeated by angels of God (Rv12) →kicked out of tabernacle & broken into pieces \"Holy City, new Jerusalem\" New tabernacle which is created by Jesus & 12 disciples as cornerstones (Jn14:3) Consists of martyr spirits of those beheaded because of God's word & testimony of Jesus \"Prepared as bride\" To symbolize how 12 disciples & martyred spirits (brides) received seed from husband (Jesus) \"God's dwelling place\" 144.000 & GMW (Rv3:12, Rv14:1-5) \"Old order of things passed away\" Previous world (spiritual Israel) corrupted→ destroyed (Heb8:13) \"Making everything new\" Through leaves of the tree of life (Ez47:12, Rv22:1-2): Whole world Satan's image → God's image \"It is done\" Prophecy of N.T. is fulfilled (Rv21:6) [cf. O.T.: Jn19:30] \"Spring of water of life\" Pastor who possesses the word of life (Rv7:17) \"He who overcomes\" 12 blessings (Rv2+3) & God's son THOSE WHO WILL BE OUTSIDE THE HOLY CITY & GO TO SECOND DEATH \"Cowardly\" Those who are afraid of believing in prophecy & physical fulfillment (being called cult) \"Unbelieving\" Those who don't believe in the prophecy of revelation & its physical fulfillment \"Vile\" Pretending to be a believer but doing wicked things \"Murderers\" Those who kill the faiths & spirits of people by telling lies \"Sexually immoral\" Those who associate with Satan's pastor \"Practice magic arts\" Those who speak false prophecies (omens) \"Idolaters\" Those who like to worship & follow the false pastor \"Liars\" Those who tell lies about God's word & deceive (persecutors & false churches) THE APPEARANCE OF THE HOLY CITY, NEW JERUSALEM \"Great & high mountain\" Mt. Zion (Rv14) \"Wife of the Lamb\" HCNJ: Jesus (bridegroom) giving word (seed) to 12 disciples & apostles=martyrs (wife) Precious jewel, jasper, clear as crystal\" Symbolizes that holy city is flawless & spotless like jewel or jasper \"Measuring rod of gold\" Word of truth: Measure City, Gates, Walls \"City like a square\" Holy city is the temple of truth & righteousness with the same amount (quantity) of God's word \"12.000 stadia\" 12.000 people sealed in each tribe \"144 cubits thick\" There are 144 representative instructors in 12 tribes (each tribe 12 representatives) \"Man's measurement\" New John measures (=educates word) to create kingdom on earth (physical realm) as shown by angel Same as angel's measurement since man measures as he has seen from angel \"12 gates: 12pearls\" Symbolizing 12 tribes (which are newly created at time of revelation) \"Each made of single pearl\" All 12 tribes created with only one word \"Great street of the city\" Way of man's heart into which the word is flowing \"Pure gold, transparent glass\" Clean & spotless (flawless) in the heart of man \"Did not see temple\" There is no physical temple in the city→ God & Jesus became the temple in the city \"Sun & moon not needed\" No more pastors & evangelists who belong to the world! God & Jesus teach directly through OWO \"Walk by its light\" Walk path made by God: Do as God taught them (Is2:2-3) \"On no day will its gates ever be shut\" Won't be shut to the sons of light (offsprings of the day): People of God free to enter"},{"kind":"notes","page":49,"title":"Notes page 49","text":"REVELATION 22: THE TREE OF LIFE & THE MESSENGER (ANGEL) OF JESUS *Mt21:43 = Rv22:1-2 THE TREE OF LIFE & GOD'S SERVANTS \"Angel\" One of the seven angels who had the seven bowls (Rv21:9) \"Water of life\" Word of life (Dt32:1-2, Jn4:10) [Ez47:1: Threshold (mouth) of temple of God- word of life] \"River\" Hearts of the disciples or evangelists (Jn7:37-39) [4 rivers=4LC (Gn2)] \"Throne of God\" ○1 OWO: God Jesus & heaven will descend upon OWO (Rv3:12,21) ○2 Mt. Zion: Throne of God, 4LC, 24 elders (Rv14:3) \"Great street of city\" Way into which word is flowing=man's heart:God's word flows (preached) through way of man's heart 1 Then the angel showed me the river of the water of life, as clear as crystal, flowing from the throne of God and of the Lamb 2 down the middle of the great street of the city. On each side of the river stood the tree of life, bearing twelve crops of fruit, yielding its fruit every month. And the leaves of the tree are for the healing of the nations. 3 No longer will there be any curse. The throne of God and of the Lamb will be in the city, and his servants will serve him. 4 They will see his face, and his name will be on their foreheads. 5 There will be no more night. They will not need the light of a lamp or the light of the sun, for the Lord God will give them light. And they will reign for ever and ever. 6 The angel said to me, \"These words are trustworthy and true. The Lord, the God of the spirits of the prophets, sent his angel to show his servants the things that must soon take place.\" 7 \"Behold, I am coming soon! Blessed is he who keeps the words of the prophecy in this book.\" 8 I, John, am the one who heard and saw these things. And when I had heard and seen them, I fell down to worship at the feet of the angel who had been showing them to me. 9 But he said to me, \"Do not do it! I am a fellow servant with you and with your brothers the prophets and of all who keep the words of this book. Worship God!\" 10 Then he told me, \"Do not seal up the words of the prophecy of this book, because the time is near. 11 Let him who does wrong continue to do wrong; let him who is vile continue to be vile; let him who does right continue to do right; and let him who is holy continue to be holy.\" 12 \"Behold, I am coming soon! My reward is with me, and I will give to everyone according to what he has done. 13 I am the Alpha and the Omega, the First and the Last, the Beginning and the End. 14 \"Blessed are those who wash their robes, that they may have the right to the tree of life and may go through the gates into the city. 15 Outside are the dogs, those who practice magic arts, the sexually immoral, the murderers, the idolaters and everyone who loves and practices falsehood. 16 \"I, Jesus, have sent my angel to give you this testimony for the churches. I am the Root and the Offspring of David, and the bright Morning Star.\" 17 The Spirit and the bride say, \"Come!\" And let him who hears say, \"Come!\" Whoever is thirsty, let him come; and whoever wishes, let him take the free gift of the water of life. 18 I warn everyone who hears the words of the prophecy of this book: If anyone adds anything to them, God will add to him the plagues described in this book. 19 And if anyone takes words away from this book of prophecy, God will take away from him his share in the tree of life and in the holy city, which are described in this book. 20 He who testifies to these things says, \"Yes, I am coming soon.\" Amen. Come, Lord Jesus. 21 The grace of the Lord Jesus be with God's people. Amen."},{"kind":"notes","page":50,"title":"Notes page 50","text":"\"Tree of life\" The one (pastor) who possess word (seed) of life (who is born of seed of God & grown up) ○1 Person: Seed of life → many tree of life [○2 Organization] \"Bearing 12 crops of fruit, yielding fruit every month\" Each of 12 tribes opens class every month→ harvesting crops of fruit \"Leaves of tree of life\" People who have word of life → today: 144.000 \"Healing of nations\" Heal nations which were intoxicated with Satan's word (maddening wine) →must be born again of God's seed & changed to God's image \"Seeing face of God\" Seeing OWO=seeing God & Jesus because God's throne is with OWO (Jn14:9-10,Jn10:30,Jn15:18-19) \"Name on foreheads\" To show that they are all sealed with word of God (Rv14:1) \"No more night\" Those who are ignorant of God's word cannot be found inside God's temple \"Light of lamp & sun\" Word of evangelist & pastor: Not needed because God & Jesus become our lamp & sun (Rv21:23) JESUS' ADVOCATE (MESSENGER) & THOSE WHO ARE BLESSED & THOSE WHO ARE OUTSIDE THE CITY \"Blessed who keeps\" Kingdom & priests of God (Rv1:5-6, Rv5:9-10) \"Seen & heard\" New John (pastor like John the apostle): No one can testify about events of revelation except OWO \"Fellow servant\" They are all spirit of prophecy: speak on behalf of someone (Rv19:10) \"Let him continue to do wrong\" God & Jesus testified everything to them→ cannot do anything anymore (cf. Lk19:11-26) Vile & wrong → wicked → condemned to second death Righteous & holy→ reward: eternal life (1Jn2:25, Jn8:51-55, 1Cor15:51-54, Jn6:53-58, Jn5:39, 1Jn5:13) \"Wash their robes\" Wash acts & deeds with word of life flowing from throne of God & Jesus (Rv22:1-2) → Mission center Those outside the city \"Dogs\" Betrayers \"Practice magic arts\" Telling false omens or false revelation \"Sexually immoral\" Being associated with Satan's pastor & receiving word of Satan \"Murderers\" Killing faiths or spirits of believers with lies or other gospels \"Practice falsehood\" Telling lies THE MESSENGER OF JESUS & THE RESULT OF THOSE WHO ADD OR TAKE AWAY ANYTHING FROM THE BOOK OF REVELATION \"Messenger of Jesus\" Counselor/ Advocate (Jn14,15,16) [Mt24:45-47, Rv1:2, Rv10:8-10, Rv12:5, Rv21:7, Rv22:8,16] \"The Spirit\" ○1 The Spirit of truth ○2 the Spirit of Jesus \"The bride\" The wife of the Lamb = the pastor whom the spirit of Jesus is with → OWO (Rv2:26-27) Result of those who add or take away anything from this book of prophecy → Hell ○1 They will receive the plagues descried in this book (seals, trumpets, bowls) ○2 They won't have share in the tree of life and in the holy city REVELATION 21 THE NEW HEAVEN & NEW EARTH, AND THE HOLY CITY 1-8 New heaven & new earth, first heaven & first earth & sea 9-27 Appearance of the Holy City, New Jerusalem REVELATION 22 THE TREE OF LIFE & THE MESSENGER (ANGEL) OF JESUS 1-5 The tree of life & God's servants 6-15 Jesus' advocate & those who are blessed & those who are outside the city 16-21 The messenger of Jesus & the result of those who add or take away anything from book of revelation"},{"kind":"notes","page":51,"title":"Notes page 51","text":"Year Date Main Event Additional Info 1964 Hosaeng Prayer House (호생기도원) meetings for around a year Head of house:김종규 1965 November 유인구+ 7 left prayer house 1966 February Start of 100 days training Prayer meetings at Immanuel's house March 14 ESTABLISHMENT DAY OF TABERNACLE TEMPLE (장막성전) April 4 Ascend Mt Cheonggye (청계산) 7 messengers educated by holy spirit End of May: Before coming down mountain, covenant made with blood June 1-24 Construction of Tabernacle Temple building 24 days (Hag1:1,15) July Start service in temple 1967 February SSN entered Tabernacle Temple June 7 members rebelled against Immanuel & went to Songdo (송도) after ripping off covenant paper & urinating on ark of covenant Beginning of the Betrayal 1st sin (Jer2:13, Hos10:10) Samson took charge & said he is branch (Zech6:12, Jer1:11-12) After losing sun, moon loses its light 1969 Nov 30 Promised day of covenant: Nothing happened due to betrayal 3 messengers left (백만봉, 신종환, 신광일) Solomon established 'Recreation church' ('New Tabernacle church') 1970 April “Look Korea” (루크코리아) had article regarding the temple (The tabernacle was not under 유인구's name, but under his younger brother, 유인수, who had left for North Korea) Beginning of SSN’s persecution (김영애's adopted son, Nehemiah, tried to stab SSN to death) 1971 March 14  SSN went back to his hometown due to \"Look Korea\" issue  Construction of the New Temple (around 400 square feet) 탁성환 introduces 오평호 and 유재열 to each other at Seoul Station 1975 오평호 entered the Tabernacle ~1980: Formation of Stewardship Education Center (청지기교육원) 2nd sin (Jer2:13, Hos10:10) 1977 Autumn SSN appointed by Jesus at Cheongdo Hyeonri Bridge (청도 현리교) Start of events in Book of Revelation (Rv1:9-20) 1979 SSN sent letters to 7 churches on behalf of Jesus (Rev2-3) 1980 Spring SSN receives the opened scroll (Rv10) March 14 오평호 became a chairman/head pastor of tabernacle ~ Sept14. 1/4 of earth killed (Rv6:7-8) Eradication of cults (heresy) ordered by president 전두환 → Authority given to Stewardship Education Center: 탁성환 Sept 14 TABERNACLE NAME CHANGED TO ISAAC PRESBYTERIAN CHURCH (Rv6:12-17) Beginning of Destruction Period (42 months)  Resignation of all positions of the tabernacle  10 horns (elders) appointed by Presbyterian law  정창래, 김창도, 김영애 left October  유재열 left for United States for pastor certificate (Rv12: Desert)  오평호 is kicked out of Tabernacle due to evangelists (Rv17:8)  Two witnesses are imprisoned for 98 days: No one would testify Silence for 30 minutes: 6months 1980.09.14-1981.03.14 (Rv8:1) 1981 Feb 2 SSN released from jail (~January 30: Police let them go) Verdict: Suspended Sentence (Death of 2 witnesses: Rv11) 3 1/2 days: January 30 - February 2 After 3 days he went back to tabernacle (Resurrection: Rv11,Rv1:7) March 14 OWO + remnant seed start having services on mountains Continued for 3 years Golden censer (Rv8:3-5) Gathered by Sea of Glass (Rv15:1-4) April~May 오평호 becomes S.E.C. Secretary General → Returns to tabernacle (Help of 2horns:Rv13:11) (5th trumpet:Rv9) (Out of Abyss:Rv17:8) Begin of 150 days of flood (~Sept 20) (Gen7:24) (Rv9:4-5) Sept Some evangelists sentenced to 10 days probation (Rv2:10) Sept 20 2pm Ordination Service (Hour, Day, Month, Year: Rv9:15) Receiving mark of the beast (Rv13) 17 evangelists set up as idols (Rv13:15) 4 Angels (Rv9:15): 유재열, 오평호, 탁성환, 김정두"},{"kind":"notes","page":52,"title":"Notes page 52","text":"Year Date Main Event Additional Info 1983 The Tabernacle Temple (physical building) was torn down forcibly 1984 February  Event of Aaron’s Golden Calf: 홍종효 (one of 2 witnesses), 신문배 (one of 4 horses)  25 people betrayed as group (Ez8:16, Ez11: Group of 신문배) Death of 유인구 March 14 ESTABLISHMENT OF TEMPLE OF TABERNACLE OF TESTIMONY (신천지예수교 증거장막성전) (RV15:5) Start of 7th Trumpet 7 Bowls of Wrath (1984-1991) (Rv13:10, Rv18:6) April  유재열 returns from United States  오평호 leaves (Rv17:8,11) June 3 First official SCJ service at Bisan-dong (비산동) August “Is 탁명환 a Shaman (박수무당)?” Article regarding truth of Stewardship Education Center published Wrath of God (Rv16) Sept 24 1984.3.14 was declared as foundation date of God's kingdom 24th day of 9th month (Hag2:10-19) 1985 신종환 declared that신광일is 2nd Jesus → left SCJ 1986 March 오평호 returned to Korea & tabernacle SSN’s domestic pilgrimage to take photos of Tabernacle Temple Asian Game: Happenings in Tabernacle Temple were let known Bowl of Wrath (Rv16) 1987  오평호 resigned from the tabernacle  홍종효 (Reed: Rv11) left SCJ 1988 Olympics: Happenings in the Tabernacle Temple were let known Wrath (Rv16) 1990 Establishment of first mission center in Sadang (사당) Invited to wedding banquet (Rv19) Zion theology center (Rv14) 1991 April 1 Zion center has 1st class graduation: First 12 fruits 1995 March 14 Establishment of the throne: 7 leaders of education, 12 tribe leaders, 24 elders 12 tribes created (Rv7, Rv14) 1996 SSN makes pilgrimage to Israel/Turkey 1997 December Tribe leader of Thaddaeus tribe (신정용) betrayed Betrayal of 1 of the 12 (Rv7) 1998 New Jerusalem Emblem patent was registered (#42-001873) 1999 SCJ HQ moved to the city of Gwacheon (과천시) 2000 Zion Mission Center Emblem patent was registered (#0461741) 2002 SCJ Website created 2010 Start of SCJ Open Bible Seminar 2012 Sept 16 The World Peace Festival: 6th Sports and Culture Celebration of Restoring Light (제6회 세계평화광복 하늘문화예술체전) First time foreigners invited World Peace Tour 2013 May 25 Declaration of World Peace (World Peace Gate in Seoul Olympic Park) World Peace Walk 2014 Sept 17-19 World Alliance of Religions’ Peace (WARP) Summit (종교대통합만국회의) All nations come & worship (Rv15) Healing all nations (Rv22) 2984 March 14 WHITE THRONE JUDGMENT"}];
